Inkinga emabandleni aseHarlem: Tinsimbi taseSt. Martin tithule phakadze
Adams utsi: "Bantfu labadzala lengikhulume nabo batsi bekunetindzawo tekudlela kanye netemasontfo edolobheni".
Kodvwa nyalo sekute ngisho namunye.
Kuphela kwetindzawo tekubhadla kungaphindze kucaciswe:
Indlela yekukhulumisana seyishintjile.
"Lelibhara alizange selifane nendlu yekuhlala yesifundza lebesivame kuya kuyo".
Kodvwa lokwesabisako ngemaSontfo kutsi imali letsengwe ngekutsengisa tintfo tabo angeke yanele, ngisho nobe baholi bawo betsembela kangakanani.
Wengeta watsi, indzawo yeliSontfo itawuba yindlu lenetindlu letinyenti, futsi bantfu labatawuhlala kuyo angeke bakhone kusekela emasontfo lasasele kulendzawo.
Adams utsi: "Bantfu labanyenti labatawutsenga letindlu batawuba ngulabamhlophe, futsi loko kutawusenta kutsi emasontfo lafana nalawa avale ngobe bomakhelwane babo labasha angeke babe ngemalunga elibandla".
Totimbili letinsontfo takhiwa ngemabandla lamhlophe ngaphambi kwekutsi iHarlem ibe yindzawo yebantfu labamnyama: iMetropoliten Community nga-1870, bese kutsi iSontfo iSt. Martin  lakhiwa ngemuva kweminyaka lelishumi.
Bantfu bekucala labatsatsa lisontfo lema Methodist bahamba ngemnyaka wa 1930.
Lesakhiwo sabo satfolwa ngumphristi lomnyama lobekahlala eceleni kwabo.
Ngesikhatsi lisontfo laseSt. Martin selitfola bantfu labamnyama, laholwa nguMfundisi John Howard Johnson, lowahlela kutsi kuvalwe titolo letise 125th Street, lokuyindlela lenkhulu yekutsengisa eHarlem, lapho khona bantfu labamnyama bebangavunyelwa kutsi basebente nobe batfutfukiswe.
Nga-1939 umlilo wabulala lelikhaya, futsi ngesikhatsi sekuvuselelwa, bafundisi ba-Johnson bacela kutsi kufakwe i-carilion.
Umfundisi David Johnson, indvodzana ya-Johnson, lowamlandzela njengenhloko yeSontfo lase St. Martin, abetigcabha ngekubita le-carillon ngekutsi 'tinsimbi tebantfu labaphuyile'.
Kodvwa lowati kahle lowahlola le-carilion ngaJulayi, wayibita ngalenye indlela: "Lifa Lelisiko" kanye "Nentfo Lemcoka Yemlandvo".
Tati letivela eNyuvesi yaseMichigan, Tiffany Ng, nato tatsi le-carillon leseSontfweni laseSt. Martin, yaba yinsimbi yekucala emhlabeni leyadlalwa ngumculi lomnyama, Dionisio A. Lind. Eminyakeni lengu-18 leyendlulile, wamenywa kutsi adlale i-carillon lenkhulu eSontfweni laseRiverside.
Ngekusho kwaMerriwezer, lisontfo laseSt. Martin lisengakalitfoli lelinye.
Etinyangeni letimbalwa letimbalwa letengcile, kwakhiwe simo lesimatima ngelisontfo laseSt. Martin, lapho kwakhiwe khona takhi netisebenti, letinye tato betimenywe baholi beliSontfo, letinye betimenywe libandla le-Episcopal.
Umhlangano webaholi belibandla, lokuyinhlangano lelawulako, lebeyifaka ekhatsi baholi bemhlaba, ngaJulayi wabhenela kulelidolobha, wakhombisa kukhatsateka ngekutsi leli dolobha litawutama kuhocisa tindleko temsebenti kumhlangano webaholi, nanobe laba bebangakahlosi kukhetsa bakhi kanye nebakhiciti lebebatfunyelwe nguleli dolobha.
