Sainsbury uhlela kuhlupha imakethe yetinongo tase Britain
Sainsbury utawuvula tindzawo tekugcobisa kanye netiphunga etitolo letinguBoots, Superdrag kanye neDebenhams, kanye netikhungo tekugcobisa, lokutintfo letitawusebenta njengetitolo letitsengisa tintfo letitfolakalako.
I-UK's Perfume and Cosmetics market, lelinganiselwa ku-£2.8 billion, iyachubeka nekukhula, kantsi imfashini netintfo tekusebenta ekhaya tiyahhohloka.
Banikati betitolo batfola tintfo tekugcwalisa emashalofu labekadze agcinelwe kubuka ema-TV, ema-microwave, tintfo tasekhaya, futsi kutsenga emaphaphamtini kanye netintfo tekutilungisa kubonakala kuyindlela lekahle.
Ngekusho kwebasebenti ba Sainsbury, kuhlelwe kutsi kukhuliswe kabili inombolo yetintfo tekuhloba kute kube ngu-3 000; lokufaka ekhatsi kwekucala kutsi kuniketwe emabhodi lafana ne Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman kanye ne Dr. PawPaw.
Lokusekhona lokukhona kwaL'Oreal, Maybelline kanye ne Burt's Bees kutawukhishwa ngalokukhulu, etindzaweni letikhetsiwe, ngendlela yekuhlela tintfo etitolo te Booth.
Ngetulu kwaloko, luhlu lwemikhicito ye-Boutique Cosmetics lutawuhlelwa kabusha lube yimikhicito ye-vegan kute kuhlangabetwane netidzingo tebantfu labasha.
Tindlu letimbili taseSainsbury titawuba netitolo te-Fragrance Shop: kwekucala kwavuleka e-Croydon, eningizimu yeLondon, ngeliviki leliphelile, bese kutsi kwesibili kulindzeleke kutsi kuvule e-Selly Oak, eBirmingham, kulomnyaka.
Tintfo letenteka ku-Internet kanye nekutsenga tintfo letincane letitsengwa malanga onkhe etitolo letincane letisedvute nemakhaya, kwenta kutsi timakethe titfole letinye tindlela tekutsengisa.
Mike Coop, longumengameli weSainsbury's utsi tindzawo tekutsengisela titfutfuka tibe titolo letikhulu, kantsi netitolo takhe letinkhulu tifuna kubambana netitolo letincane letifana na-Aldi naLiddle, ngekuniketa tinsita letinyenti kanye netintfo letingasito tekudla.
Emakhulu etitolo letinkhulu taseSainsbury tinetitolo te-Argos, futsi letinye tato nyalo setitfolakala etitolo te-Habitates kusukela letitolo titfole lamabhadi eminyakeni lemibili leyengcile, lokuholele ekukhuleni kwekutsengiswa kwekudla kanye nemali lengenako ngenca yaloko lokutsengiwe.
Imetamo leyake yentiwa ngulesitolo sekuphakamisa luhlaka lwayo kanye neyekuhambisa emaphilisi ayizange iphumelele.
Ekucaleni kwemnyaka wa 2000 kwacalwa kusebenta ndzawonye kwa Sainsbury na Boots, kepha ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi kwavela kungevani emkhatsini walaba labatsintsekako mayelana nekwabelana ngemali lengenako ngekutsengisa tintfo tekwelapha etitolo.
Lendlela lensha yavela ngemuva kwekutsengiswa kwe Sainsbury's Pharmaceutical Business (lokunetitolo letingu 281) ku Selesio, umnikati we Lloyd's Pharmacy, ngemali lengemarandi latigidzi leti-125 eminyakeni lemitsatfu leyengcile.
Lloyds kulindzeleke kutsi asekele kuphumelelisa loluhlelo ngekutsi afake imikhicito leminingi yekunakekela sikhumba ye La Roche-Posay ne Vichy etitolo letine.
Paul Mills-Hicks, longumphatsi wekutsengisa eSainsbury's utsi: "Sente lushintjo lolukhulu ekubukekeni nasekufuneni tintfo letinemakha kanye netintfo tekwenta tintfo kute sikwati kwenta bantfu labatsengako babe nemoya lomuhle.
Siphindze sicele beluleki labaceceshiwe labatawuhlala bakulungele kusisita.
Lendlela yetfu yekutsengisa, indlela yetfu yekwakha kanye netindzawo letisebentisekako letitawujabulisa bantfu labanyenti labafuna tintfo tekugcoka kanye nemakha.
Peter Jones "watfukutsela" ngekuphuma kwaHolly Willoughby kuloluhlelo lwemali lengemarandi latigidzi leti-11
Peter Jones, inkanyezi yeLogos Dragon, utfukutsele ngekuphuma kwaHolly Willoughby ku-£11 million lebekatsandza kuyenta ne-Peter's lifestyle brand, kepha esikhundleni saloko wakhetsa kuhlanganyela na-Marks & Spencer kanye ne-ITV.
Willowby ute sikhatsi sekwenta tintfo tasekhaya kanye netintfo tekusebenta nabo.
Lelibhizinisi lalabashadikazi belifaniswa ne Goop brand ya Gwyneth Paltrow.
Lomsakazi loneminyaka lengu-37 budzala wamemetela sincumo sakhe ku-Instagram ekuseni.
Sincumo saHolly Willoughby sekushiya umkhicito wabo lozuzisako kute agcine sekente tivumelwano letinsha naMarks naSpencer kanye ne-ITV, saletsa intfukutselo yaPeter Jones, inkanyezi yeLogo Dragon.
Ngekusho kwemitfombo yetfu, Jones "watfukutsela" ngesikhatsi umbukisi lotsandvwako emhlanganweni lobalulekile lobewubanjwe ngaLesibili enhloko hhovisi yebhizinisi yakhe eMarlow, Buckinghamshire, avuma kutsi ngemuva kwekwenta tivumelwano letinsha letibita tigidzi leti-1.5, angeke abe nesikhatsi lesenele semikhiqizo yabo yekugcoka kanye netintfo tekusebenta ekhaya iTruly.
Lelophawu laWillough belicatsaniswa neGoop, lekungumntfwana wemlingisi Gwyneth Paltrow, futsi bekulindzeleke kutsi kutsengiswa kwalo kwente imali yaWilloughby ibe kabili, lokusho kutsi imali yakhe lelinganiselwa kutigidzi leti-11 temarandi.
Umsakazi loneminyaka lengu 37 budzala wamemetela ngekushiya kwakhe ku-Instagram, kantsi naJones ushiye i-UK ngendiza yangasese aya kulelinye lalama-villa akhe.
Lomunye umbiko utsi, i-Truly brand beyimcoka kakhulu kuHolly.
Bekulitsemba lelisetulu lekutsi utawuphila iminyaka leminyenti.
Lesincumo sakhe sabangela kutsi bonkhe bantfu labatsintsekako bangaboni lutfo.
Bonkhe bebatfukutsele kakhulu ngaLesibili ngobe bekusele emaviki lambalwa kutsi kusungulwe lelibhande lemikhumbi.
Emahhovisi etfu lamakhulu aseMarlow, besekunelifu leligcwele tintfo lebetitawutsengiswa.
Tati titsi kuhamba kwa-This Morning, lomunye wetinkhanyeti letatiwako taseBrithani, kungenta le-ejensi ibe netindleko letitigidzi temaphawundi ngenca yetindleko letinkhulu letitsatfwa etintfweni letifaka ekhatsi emakhushini, emakhandlela, timphahla kanye nekubambezeleka kwekusebenta.
Ngetulu kwaloko, loku kusho kutsi buhlobo lobusendvulo sebuphelile.
Njengobe bakhulisa bantfwana labatsatfu, boWillobie nendvodza yabo Dan Baldwin, bebasebangani naJones nemkakhe, Tara Cappe, iminyaka lelishumi.
Willowby wasungula i-truly brand kanye naTara Capp nga 2016, kantsi nendvodza yaTara, Peter Jones, loneminyaka lengu 52, waba ngumholi wenkapani ngaMashi.
Bobabili labashadile bavame kuvakasha ndzawonye, futsi ngetulu kwaloko, Jones unebamba 40% walabantfu labatsengisako ku Dan Baldwin's TV production firm.
Willowby utawuba ngummeli we M&S futsi utawutsatsa sikhundla sa Anthony McPartlin njengemshicileli we-ITV I'm a Celebrity.
Umuntfu losondzelene naJones watsi: "Singeke sikhulume ngetintfo takhe tekutsengisa".
Kwaba matima kucocisana, kodvwa ekugcineni sacala kutsandzana.
Wenta bulima ngekugceka kutsi utawugcwala etinhlelweni temitfombo yetindzaba ngenca yekusho kwakhe kutsi "umengameli akafaneleki" kanye nekuhlola kwakhe kahle umholi waseNyakatfo Korea.
Kungani Mengameli Trump angavumi kutsi kube netinsolo letinyenti kangaka?
Kusho Trump, alingisa livi lememeteli.
"Angizange ngivume lutfo".
Waphindze watsi Kim Jong-un unesifiso sekuhlangana futsi ngemuva kwekutsi Trump abite umhlangano wabo wekucala lowabanjelwa eSingapore ngaJuni ngekutsi kusinyatselo lesibalulekile sekunciphisa tikhali te-nuclear taseNyakatfo Korea.
Kodvwa tinkhulumiswano tekulwa nekusebentisa emabutfo enyukliya atizange tiphumelele.
Ngemuva kwetinyanga letintsatfu kuhlangene eSingapore ngaJuni, lisikhulu sepolitiki saseNyakatfo Korea, Lee Yong Ho, sakhuluma nebaholi bemhlaba eMhlanganweni weMhlabuhlangene ngeMgcibelo, satsi iNyakatfo Korea isalindzele "kuphindzisela lokukahle" lokuvela eMelika ngemuva kwekucedza i-DPRK.
Esikhundleni saloko, i-US, kusho leliphoyisa, ichubeka nekusebentisa letijeziso njengendlela yekucindzetela.
Ngesikhatsi ahlangana nebalandzeli bakhe, Mengameli Trump waveta umbono loncono kakhulu.
"Tintfo tihambe kahle neNorth Korea", washo njalo.
Besisemaphetselweni emphini neNyakatfo Korea.
Tigidzi tebantfu betingafa.
Nyalo sesinebudlelwane lobuhle.
Ngekusho kwaTrump, imetamo yakhe yekulungisa budlelwane naKim Jong-un yaletsa titselo: kuvivinywa kwemakhemikhali kwacedvwa, batfunjwa bakhululwa futsi emasotja aseMelika labesele eNingizimu Korea abuyela ekhaya.
Akhuluma ngebudlelwane bakhe naKim Jong-un, Trump wagcizelela kutsi kute lokumangalisako endleleni yakhe yekusebenta ngekwebufundisi.
"Kutiphatsa kahle njengemengameli kumelula, kepha esikhundleni sebantfu labangu-10 000 labasemgwacweni labahlasela lelihholo leligcwele bantfu, bekutawuba nebantfu labangu-200", kwasho Trump, akhomba sicumbi sebantfu labesembikwakhe.
Tsunami kanye nekutamatama kwemhlaba e-Indonesia: Kubhujiswa lokukhulu, bantfu babulawa ngema-cents
Emalangeni ekucala ngemuva kwekutamatama kwemhlaba lokwahlasela iLombok, tinhlangano letingekho ngaphansi kwahulumende tangaphandle tatjelwa kutsi asikho sidzingo sekusita.
Nanobe bantfu labangetulu kwa-10% baseLombok baphelelwe tindlu, hulumende akazange akubone kubalulekile kutsi amemetele inhlekelele yemvelo, lokuyintfo lebalulekile kute kutfolakale lusito lwemave emhlaba.
Kunyenti lokubuhlungu kutsi bakwenta kwacaca kutsi abakudzingi kusekelwa ngemave ngemave, ngako bekungasimelula,  kusho Selina Sambung.
Inhlangano letsi "Khulula Bantfwana" ilungiselela kutsi licembu layo litfunyelwe ePalu, kodvwa asati kutsi licembu langaphandle lingakhona yini kusebenta khona.
Ngekusho kwaMnu. Sutopo, ummeli we-National Disaster Management Authority, hulumende wase-Indonesia uhlola simo ePalu kute abone kutsi ngabe kungasita yini kusebentisa tinhlangano temave emhlaba.
Njengobe i-Indonesia ihlale inetinkinga tekutamatama kwemhlaba, solo ayikalungeli kahle.
Nanobe kwakhiwe tindzawo tekukhosela ema-tsunami e-Acheche, atikavami kutfolakala kulamanye emabhange.
Nanobe bekunelulekiso lwekubhujiswa yi-tsunami, iPalu ayizange ivule umsindvo wekwecwayisa bantfu, futsi loko kungenteka kwabangela kutsi kube netigidzi tebantfu labafile.
Kutfutsa emkhatsini wetihlenge letinyenti tase-Indonesia kuyinkinga ngisho nasesikhatsini lesimnandzi.
Tinhlekelele temvelo tenta kube matima kakhulu kutsi kube nekuhleleka.
