Video: Umdlali weLiverpool Daniel Sturridge ucatsanisa inombolo emdlalweni lowalwa neChelsea ngekushaya umgomo ekhoneni lelisetulu lemnyango
Daniel Sturridge wasindzisa iLiverpool ekuhlulweni emaminithini langu-89 emdlalo we-Premier League lowalwa ne-Chelsea, lowabanjwa ngaMgcibelo e-Stamford Bridge.
Sturridge watfola kudluliswa nguJordan Shakiri cishe ngemamitha langu-27 esangweni lase Chelsea ngesikhatsi licembu lakhe lilahlekelwa ngu 1-0.
Waya ngesancele futsi wafike wabhodla ekhoneni lelingemuva lalesango.
Lelibhola lagijima lalibeka etulu, lafika lawela ekhoneni lelisetulu kakhulu.
Umgadli weligoli, Kepa Arrisbalaghe, wagxumela ebholeni, kodvwa besekwendlule sikhatsi.
Kulenkhulumo yakhe ne LiverpoolFC.com, Sturridge watsi: "Bekungumsebenti wami kutsi ngikhone kutfola ibhola, badlali labafana na Shaq bahlala badlala kakhulu ekuhlaseleni, ngako bengifuna kutinika sikhatsi lesinyenti".
"Ngabona Kante eta kimi, ngalibamba futsi ngekushesha ngalibamba".
Ngekusho kwekugcina kwemdlalo, licembu le-Chelsea belihola libanjwa licala 1-0, ligoli laletfwa ngumdlali waseBelgium, Eden Azar, emaminithini langu-25.
Umgadli losemkhatsini weChelsea, wanika Matteo Kovacic liphasela, wawela emkhatsini wenkambu waya eLiverpool.
Kovacic wadlala umdlalo wakhe ngekutsintsa linye.
Wase udlulisela liphasela ku-Azar, lowahamba waya esangweni.
Azar wabadlula labadlali labamvikelako futsi wahlasela umgadli weLiverpool Alison Becker, washaya ekhoneni lelikhashane.
Liverpool itawuhlangana ne Napoli esigabeni semacembu e-Champions League. Lomdlalo utawudlala eSan Paolo Stadium eNapol (Italy) ngalesitsatfu ntsambama ngensimbi yesitsatfu.
"I-Chelsea itawudlala ne-VideoTon emdlalweni we-UEFA Euroleague lotawubanjwa ngaLesine eLondon, futsi ngensimbi yesitsatfu ntsambama".
Linani lebantfu labafa ngenca yeluswatsi e-Indonesia selikhuphuke laba ngu-832
Linani lebantfu labafa ngenca yekutamatama kwemhlaba kanye ne-tsunami lelandzela e-Indonesia selikhuphuke lafika ku-832, kusho i-National Disaster Management Authority ngeLisontfo ekuseni.
Ngekusho kwaSutopo Purvo Nugroho, sikhulumi seliTiko lesitsite enkhulumeni yelubiko, kutamatama kwemhlaba lokwenteka ngaLesihlanu kwabangela tsunami lebeyiphakeme ngemamitha langu-6, futsi bantfu labanyenti basele ngaphansi kwetakhiwo letishelelekile.
Lidolobha lasePalu, lelinebantfu labangetulu kwetinkhulungwane letingu-380, lagcwala tindzala.
Emaphoyisa abambe indvodza leneminyaka lengu-32 budzala, leyasolwa ngekugwaza umfati.
Umtimba wemfati watfolakala eBirkenhead, eMercedes, ekuseni, futsi kuphenywa ngelicala lekubulala.
Umtimba wemfati loneminyaka lengu-44 budzala lobanetigebengu watfolakala ngensimbi yemfica ekuseni ngesikhatsi kushaywa umfati wakhe, e-Graison Meuse, John Street.
Emaphoyisa afuna bantfu labangafakaza ngalomgodzi.
O'Hagan, umhloli wetebulungiswa utsi: "Loluphenyo lusesigabeni sekucala, kodvwa ngicela wonkhe umuntfu lobekasendzaweni yaseJohn Street eBirkenhead futsi lobone nobe weva lokutsite lokungavakali, kutsi asitsintse".
Ngiphindze ngicele bonkhe bantfu, ikakhulukati bashayeli bematekisi, labakhona kutfola lokutsite ku-video, kutsi batfumele nobe ngabe nguwuphi umniningwane longabasita kuloluphenyo.
Sikhulumi semaphoyisa sicinisekise kutsi lomuntfu lobulawe abehlala eBirkenhead futsi umtimba wakhe watfolakala endzaweni lebeyikhashane.
Bantfu labacabanga kutsi bayamati lomuntfu bafika lapha kulendzawo lamuhla ntambama kute babute imibuto mayelana nekutsi utfolwe kuphi.
Kuphenya kuyachubeka futsi emaphoyisa alungiselela kutjela tihlobo taloshonile.
Umshayeli welitiko letatekisi lohlala e-Graison Meuse wetama kungena endlini yakhe, kodvwa emaphoyisa amtjela kutsi kute umuntfu lovunyelwe kungena nobe kuphuma kulesakhiwo.
Watsi nakeva ngaloko lokwenteka, wehluleka kukhuluma.
Bantfu labahlala kuleyondlu batjelwe kutsi angeke bakhone kubuyela emakhaya abo sikhatsi lesidze.
Lenye yetindvuna temaphoyisa yatjela lomuntfu kutsi lendzawo yonkhe leyayisendzaweni yakhe beyingaba yindzawo lebhekene nebugebengu.
Lomunye wesifazane wakhala.
"Kwesabeka kakhulu!" washo njalo.
Nga-2 emini, emabhasi lamabili emaphoyisa afika endzaweni, futsi lelinye lahlala ngaphandle kwendzawo lebiyelwe.
Emaphoyisa lamanyenti abekwe ngekhatsi kulesakhiwo kute agadze.
Bonkhe labanelwati bacelwe kutsi batfumele umlayeto ku-Twitter ku- @MerPolCC, bashayele ku-101 nobe batfumele umlayeto ku-Crimestoppers ngekungabonakali ku-0800 555 111 (licala 247 langamhlaka-30 Septhemba).
