Umlimi waseShayina walunywa yingulube lebulalako
Umlimi wabulawa yingulube emakethe lese ningizimu nshona yase China, kubika bomasiko.
Umtimba walomuntfu lobekabulewe (lokukhulunywa ngaye kuphela etinhlelweni, Yuán) lobekabulewe umchamo watfolwa eceleni kwesinkhwa emakethe yaseLupanshuy, esifundzeni saseGuizhou, eningizimu yeChina, kubika iphephandzaba i-Morning Post ngeLisontfo.
Umfuyi wetingulube ulungiselela kugoma tingulube takhe epulazini, May 30, 2005, eSinin, esifundzeni saseChinhai, eChina.
Yuan nemzala wakhe befika bevela esifundzeni lesisedvute sase Yunnan ngaLwesitsatfu futsi batfumela tingulube letingu-15 kutsi titewutsengiswa.
Ngakusasa ekuseni umzala wakhe watfola sidvumbu sa-Yuan singakaphefumuli, kantsi umnyango wasesigodlweni setingulube sasedvute wawungakavulwa.
Kulendlu yetingulube bekunemgodzi lomkhulu lobekachoboshele ingati.
Kuhlolwa kwetilwane letincane kwaveta kutsi ingulube lebeyibeseyinesisindvo lesingu-250 kg, yaluma lomlimi yaze yafa.
"Tinyawo temnaketfu betihlotjisiwe futsi tigcwele ingati", kusho Wu, sihlobo salona lofile, ku-Guiyang Evening News.
I-video yekugadza ibonise kutsi Yuan waya emakethe ngensimbi yesine ekuseni kute ondle tilwane takhe.
Umtimba watfolwa ngemuva kwelihora.
Ingulube leyabulala labanye beyingasiyo yebantfwana.
Umphatsi walomakethe watjela i-Evening News kutsi lengulube ibekwe yedvwa ngesikhatsi seluphenyo kute kuvikelwe kutsi ingaphindze ihlaseleke.
Kubikwa kutsi umndeni wa-Yuan usetinkhulumisanweni nebaphatsi bemakethe mayelana nekuniketwa sincephetelo sekufa kwalomlimi.
Kuhlasela kwetingulube kubantfu akwenteki kakhulu.
Nga-2016, ingulube yahlasela umfati nendvodza yakhe epulazini laseMassachusetts, eMelika, futsi yalimala kakhulu lendvodza.
Eminyakeni lelishumi leyendlulile, silwane lesisindzako lesingu-300 kg sabopha umlimi waseWales satsi usengakatfutsi, samkhulula ngobe besesaba umfati wakhe.
Nga-2012, umlimi wase Oregon eMelika wafaka sicelo sekudliwa tingulube takhe, umlimi wase Canada watjela iCBC News kutsi tingulube ativami kuba neludlame, kepha kunambitseka kwengati kungenta kutsi tilwane tibe neludlame.
