Siphepho iRosa sitawuletsa imvula lenkhulu eningizimu-nshonalanga yeMelika
Ngekusho kwesiphrofetho, iSiphepho Rosa siyaphelelwa ngemandla njengobe sichamuka endzaweni lenemanti lapholile siya ngaselugwini lolusenyakatfo yeMexico.
Nobe kunjalo, kulamalanga lambalwa letako, itawuletsa imvula netikhukhula enyakatfo yeMexico naseningizimu-nshonalanga yeMelika.
NgeMgcibelo, 5 ekuseni eNew York, lesiphepho sesifinyelele esigabeni sekucala, sinemoya lofika ku-135 km/h, sisendzaweni lengemakhilomitha langu-360 eningizimu-nshonalanga yelidolobha lasePunta-Euchenia (eMexico).
Kulindzeleke kutsi lelichingasiphepho lisuke enyakatfo ngeLisontfo.
Ngesikhatsi lesifanako, indzawo lenemandla laphansi itawucala kwakheka ngetulu kweLwandle Lwelwandle LwasePacific, futsi itawuya emphumalanga kuya elugwini lolusentshonalanga yaseMelika.
NgeMsombuluko, iMexico ilindzelwe kutsi inisele ngemasentimitha langu-25.
Ngenca yemfutfo wetimvula letincane letisendzaweni, imvula lenkhulu ilindzeleke kutsi yehle eningizimu-nshonalanga.
Kunemvula lencane lengaba ngemasentimitha langu-2,5 kuya kulangu-10 letawubangela tikhukhula letinemandla, kudvuma kwematje kanye nekukhukhuleka kwemhlaba.
Kuletinye tindzawo, ikakhulukati eningizimu yase Nevada nase Arizona, ngenca yemoya lonomswakama kakhulu, lizinga lemvula lingangetulu kwemasentimitha lasihlanu kuya kulasiphohlongo ngelihora.
Etindzaweni letitsite letise ningizimu nshona yase USA, ikakhulu endzaweni lenkhulu yase Arizona, kulindzeleke kutsi kube nemvula lengaba ngu 510 cm.
Ingoti yetikhukhula letisheshako ngenca yekwehla kwetimvula letishisako.
Njengobe kunematfuba lamanyenti ekutsi kube netimvula, kuhamba ngetinyawo ehlane kungaba nemiphumela lemibi.
Tintfwala tingenta imifula ibe nemanti lamakhulu, futsi kudvuma kungabangela umoya lomkhulu futsi kuvuse litulu.
Njengobe lesigaba sekucindzeteleka lokuncane sicala, kutawuba nemvula lenkhulu etindzaweni letiseceleni kwelugwini lwaseNingizimu California.
Kungaba nemvula lengaba ngemasentimitha langu-1.5, lokungabangela kugeleta kwematje kanye netindlela letishelelayo.
Lena yimvula yekucala kusukela ngesikhatsi semvula kulesifundza.
Emagagasi lamakhulu emvula atawugeleta e-Arizona ngeLisontfo kusihlwa nangekusasa ngeMsombuluko, bese asakateka nakuletinye tindzawo kusihlwa nangeLisontfo ekuseni.
NgaLesibili, timvula titoshona endzaweni yaseTinkhundleni Letine futsi titawuchubeka kudzimate kube nguLwesitsatfu kusihlwa.
Nga-October, simo selitulu sitawehla kakhulu eMelika ngenca yekushisa lokuncane e-Arctic kanye nekushisa lokukhulu etindzaweni letishisako.
Ngaletinye tikhatsi, loku kuholela ekushiseni lokukhulu endzaweni lencane.
Lokushisa lokwehla kakhulu kutawubonakala eMelika ngeLisontfo.
Kukhona umehluko lobukhulu emkhatsini welizinga lekushisa eKansas City (eMissouri) ne-Omaha (eNebraska), kanye naphakathi kweSt. Louis neDe Moines (eIowa).
Emalangeni lambalwa letako, kushisa kwelihlobo kutawuchubeka futsi kusakateke nakulamanye emave.
Etindzaweni letinyenti letisemkhatsini nase mphumalanga yeMelika, simo selitulu sitawushisa kusukela nga-Oktoba, emazinga ekushisa atawufika kuma-degree langetulu kwa-27 endzaweni lesuka eSouthern Plains kuya eNyakatfo Mpumalanga.
E-New York, lizinga lekushisa lingakhuphuka liyewufika ku-27°C ngaLesibili, lokusho kutsi kutawuba ngu-10°C ngetulu kwelizinga lelisemkhatsini.
Simo selitulu setfu sesikhatsi lesidze sitjela kutsi kutawuba nekushisa lokukhulu kakhulu etigodzini letise mphumalanga yeMelika kuze kube semkhatsini wenyanga ya-Okthoba.
Kulalelwa kwelicala leMengameli Brett Kavanaugh kubukwe bantfu labangetulu kwetigidzi letingu-20
Baphikisi lababili, Brett Kavanaugh naChristina Blaise Ford, labamangalela Kavanaugh ngekuhlukunyetwa ngemnyaka wa 1980, batfola kubukwa ngetindlela letisitfupha letingu 20 million ngeLesine.
Umphikiswano wepolitiki mayelana nekugunyazwa kwaKavanaw wacala ngalokungakalindzeleki, ngaLesihlanu, kwavela umlayeto lobalulekile etinhlelweni temphakatsi: Umuntfu weRiphabhulikhi Jeff Flake wafaka umbanti wekutsi emacala labekwe lona mmeli aphenye yi-FBI liviki linye.
Njengobe Ford asho ngesikhatsi etfula licala lakhe eKomidini yeTemtsetfo yeSigungu Lesibusako, ucinisile kutsi Cavanaugh wamhlasela ngesikhatsi adzakiwe futsi wetama kumkhumula ngesikhatsi asephathini.
Kavanaugh wafakaza ngekutfukutsela, watsi ucinisile kutsi loko bekungasiko.
Ngekusho kwe-ejensi yekucwaninga i-Nielsen, imibuto lebeyibukelwa bantfu labangetulu kwetigidzi letingu-20,4 ngeLesihlanu.
I-ejensi ibuke silinganiso sematiko lasuka ku-CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel kanye ne-MSNBC.
Lamanye ema-TV lafana ne-PBS, C-SPAN ne-Fox Business Network, solo awakasekelwa.
Ngetulu kwaloko, emazinga e-Nielsen awacabangi ngaso sonkhe sikhatsi ngetibukeli letibukela ithelevishini emsebentini.
Nasi sibonelo: Umuntfu lomncane kakhulu angatsandza kubona umdlalo welibhola letinyawo nobe umcimbi we-Oscar.
Inombolo lenkhulu yetibukeli yaba se-Fox News Channel, lebeyisekela kakhulu kubekwa kwaKavanawa: kubukela kwe-senate lokwathatha lilanga lonkhe kwabukelwa bantfu labatigidzi letingu 5,69 ngekwesilinganiso, kusho i- Nielsen.
Kulesibili, i-ABC inetibonwa letitigidzi letingu 3,26.
I-CBS yabukwa bantfu labatigidzi letingu 3,1, i-NBC  2,94 million, i-MSNBC yabukwa bantfu labatigidzi letingu 2,89 kantsi i-CNN yabukwa bantfu labatigidzi letingu 2,52, kusho i-Nielsen.
Ngemuva kwekulalelwa kwalelicala, bantfu labanyenti bebangasafuni kuwuva lomtsetfo.
NgaLesihlanu bekunendzaba lemangalisako lebeyibukelwa bantfu labanyenti lebeyibukelwa bantfu labanyenti futsi lebeyibukelwa bantfu labanyenti.
Ngemuva kwekutsi lisenetha lase-Arizona, lelibukeka liyincenye ye-Republican lecondzile, litjele kutsi lifuna kusekela Khawaena, i-CNN ne-CBS bakhona kubamba kutsi ngaLesihlanu ekuseni ngesikhatsi aya emhlanganweni welikomidi letemtsetfo, Flake wahlangana nelicembu lebasebenti betenhlalakahle lebebagceka lisenetha.
Umhlaba wonkhe wambona abuka phansi, ahlaselwa bomake labatsukutsele ku-CNN.
"Ngimi lapha embikwenu", kwasho lomunye wabo.
Ucabanga kutsi ukhuluma liciniso yini kulelive?
"Ngobe wena unemandla, kantsi labanye besifazane bete emandla".
Flake waphendvula kutsi lihhovisi lakhe selivele lilungiselele sitatimende futsi utawusho loko emhlanganweni welikomidi.
Ngemuva kwema-awa lambalwa, ngesikhatsi liKomidi leTemtsetfo lilungiselela kuvuma Kwanyana kutsi abe lijaji bese liyamtfumela eSenate kutsi ayovota, tonkhe titeshi teTV betisakata lomhlangano.
Kodvwa Flake wabeka umbanti munye: kutsi i-FBI ihlolisise lamacala lamayelana nalomuntfu lotawukhetfwa ngeliviki lelitako, njengobe bekulindzeleke kutsi kwentiwe ngulabambalwa labamnyama.
Flake utsi washintja umcondvo wakhe ngenca yekungenelela kwemngani wakhe, umDemocratic Senator Chris Koons.
Wenta sincumo sekugcina ngemuva kwekukhuluma naKuns kanye nalamanye emasenethi lambalwa.
Lesincumo saFlake saba nemphumela ngobe bekubonakala kutsi emaRephabliki akanayo emavoti ekuvumela Cavanaugh ngaphandle kweluphenyo.
Ngekulandzela umtsetfo waMengameli Trump, i-FBI yacala luphenyo lwekumbeka licala Kavanaugh.
