Kushona kwaWade Sims ekudubuleni: Emaphoyisa abopha Dayton Simpson ngekusola ngekubulala umgadli weLewisiana State University
Emaphoyisa abambe indvodza lemiswe ngekubulala Wade Sims, umdlali welibhola letinyawo wase-Louisiana State University.
Emaphoyisa aseBaton Rouge atsi Dayton Simpson, loneminyaka lengu-20 budzala, waboshwa futsi waboshwa ngelicala lekubulala ngesigaba sesibili.
Emaphoyisa ashicilele ividiyo yekulwa lokwenteka emkhatsini waSims naSimpson, lapho khona Sims alahlekelwa ngulama-eyeglasses akhe.
Ngekusho kwe-WAFB, siteshi setfu sase-CBS, emaphoyisa atfole i-DNA ya-Simpson kulabobuso lobutfolwe endzaweni yekwenta bugebengu.
Ngesikhatsi aphenya Simpson wavuma kutsi wamlimata kakhulu Wade.
Ngekusho kwe-Advocate, Simpsons ubekwe inhlawulo lengu-R530 000.
Umhloli wetemphilo waseBaton Rouge waseMpumalanga wakhipha siphetfo sakhe ngaLesihlanu, watsi kufa kwakhe kwabangelwa kudutjulwa kwenhloko nentamo.
Litiko libonga Litiko Letebulungiswa LaseLouisiana, Litiko Letebulungiswa LaseLouisiana, Litiko Letebulungiswa LaseSouthern, neLuphiko Lwemaphoyisa LaseNingizimu neBantfu Basemakhaya labasize ekwenteni lolucwaningo lolubangele kutsi kubanjwe lomuntfu.
Joe Alleva, longumcondzisi wetemidlalo e-Louisiana State University, wabonga emaphoyisa ngekwenta "umsebenti lomuhle wekubamba lesigelekece".
Sims abeneminyaka lengu-20 budzala.
LoMfutfo longemamitha lamabili budze bekatalwa eBaton Rouge; babe wakhe Wayne naye wadlala e Louisiana State University.
Kulomnyaka lophelile, Sims bekahola emaphuzu langu 5.6 futsi abamba ema-2.6 ngelizinga lelisemkhatsini.
Umceceshi welicembu Will Wade washo emavi ngeLesihlanu ekuseni, watsi kufa kwa-Wade Sims kwaba "simo lesibuhlungu" futsi "kwakubangela buhlungu lobukhulu" kubo bonkhe badlali.
"Loku ngiko lebengikwesaba", kwasho umceceshi.
