Intsaba-mlilo iPopocatépetl yafaka umlotha eningizimu yelidolobha laseMexico.
NgaLesihlanu, sikhungo seMexico sekuvimbela tinhlekelele temvelo satjela bantfu kutsi bangayi kulelivulankhulu: kwakheka lokukhulu kulentaba-mlilo futsi kwakhishwa igesi lenkhulu lengu-183 ngelilanga.
Ngekusho kwalesikhungo, bekuvama kuba nekudvuma nekutfutfumela edvute nalelivulankhulu.
Kuletinye tindzawo taseMexico, njengaseSochi, basebentisi betinhlelo tekuchumana batfumela titfombe tetibuko tetimoto letinetintfo letincane letinetimphunga.
Ngemuva kwekutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla langu-7.1 Mw lokutamatama ekhatsi neMexico ngaSeptember 2017, bososayensi batfole kutsi inyoni letitsela titfukutfuku titinyatsele kakhulu emakhilomitha langu-72 eningizimu-mpumalanga yelidolobha.
Intsaba-mlilo iPopokatepetl (noma, yebakitsi, Don Goyo) yintsaba-mlilo lesebentako kusukela nga-1994.
Kubambana kwemaphoyisa nema Catalan lahlukene ngekhatsi kwelive ngaphambi kwemnyaka wekucala wencwadzi yelubandlululo
NgaLesihlanu, umhlangano wetinkhulungwane tebantfu eBarcelona, lowatinikela emnyakeni wekucala we-referendum yekuphuma kwe-Catalonia eSpain, leyahlula live laba tinhlangotsi letimbili, wahlangana nemaphoyisa kanye nebantfu labafuna kutimela; bantfu labasitfupha lababambe lichaza kuleto timphikiswano baboshwa.
Emaphoyisa abecitsa bantfu lebebabhikisha, kantsi labantfu labebagcoke buso lobumnyama bebajikijela emaphoyisa emacandza kanye nelipende, lokwakwenta kutsi kube nelutfuli lolukhulu ekhatsi neBarcelona.
Ngemuva kwekutsi emaphoyisa asebentise tiboko tekubamba sicumbi, timphikiswano tacala futsi.
Kwaphela ema-awa lamaningi, bantfu lebebasekela inkhululeko bahlabela batsi: "Singeke sikhohlwe, ngeke sicolele!" kantsi labaphikisako bebaphendvula batsi: "Asiphile iSpain!"
Ngekusho kwemitfombo yetindzaba, bantfu labangu-14 labagcine sebafike esibhedlela babulawa tifo letincane.
Nga-Oktoba 1, emnyakeni lowengcile, kwenteka inhlolovo yekuphuma kwe Catalonia eSpain, leyatsatfwa njengaleyo lengekho emtsetfweni nguhulumende waseSpain, kepha yaba yintfo lebalulekile kumacembu ekuhlukana.
I-Catalonia yavota kakhulu ngekufuna kuphuma eSpain, kepha bantfu bebangekho kakhulu ngoba bantfu labaphikisana nekuphuma kwalelive bebangafuni kuvuma.
Ngekusho kwemitfombo lesemtsetfweni yaseCatalan, bantfu labangaba ngu-1 000 balimala ngesikhatsi emaphoyisa etama kuvimbela kuvota lokwentiwa etindzaweni tekukhetsa kulelive ngemnyaka lophelile.
NgaLesihlanu, ema-separatist alala endleleni lebeyifunwa ngulabo lebebafuna kumelela emaphoyisa aseSpain kute abavimbele kutsi bangayi.
Nanobe kunjalo, lomkhosi wabanjwa, kodvwa wahamba ngalenye indlela.
Umuntfu loneminyaka lengu-68 budzala, Narsis Termes, longusomandla, lowahamba nemkakhe emhlanganweni webahlukubetwa, ukhala ngekutsi litsemba lekutsi iCatalonia itfole bukhosi liyakhula.
Umnyaka lowengcile waba ngulomunye wetintfo letibalulekile ekuphileni kwetfu.
Batali bami bakhala ngenca yenjabulo ngesikhatsi bavota kulenhlolovo, kodvwa lamuhla sesisesimeni lesimatima", kusho yena.
Kwatsi muva nje, elukhetfweni lwendzawo lwangaDisemba, emacembu e-Catalan lafuna kukhululeka eSpain atfola kuncoba lokukhulu, nanobe bekulinganiselwe, kepha kulomnyaka, inhlangano yabo ilahlekelwe balandzeli, njengobe baholi labanyenti labatiwako balenhlangano babaleka noma baboshwa, balindzele kulahlwa ngenca yendzima yabo ekuhleleni le-referendum kanye nekumenyetelwa kwayo.
Juan Puch, umshayeli wemoto loneminyaka lengu-42 budzala, lobekacopha umhlangano wekwesekela emaphoyisa, watsi kuphikisana kuyachubeka emaceleni omabili etembusave.
Wachubeka watsi: "Kucindzeteleka kuya ngekuya kukhula".
NgaLesihlanu, Oriol Junqueras, munye webaholi labasi-9 belicembu lelicondze kuhlukana lase Catalonia, lobekavalelwe ejele kusukela ekupheleni kwemnyaka lophelile, watisa ngenhloso yakhe yekugcugcutela kuba lilunga lePhalamende yaseYurophu emnyakeni lotako.
Kuhlanganyela elukhetfweni lolulandzelako lwePhalamende yaseYurophu njengalomele  yindlela lencono yekulahla kulahlekelwa kwemagugu entsandvo yelinyenti kanye nekucindzetelwa nguhulumende waseSpain,  usho njalo.
