Lelicembu laGerard aliphumelelanga kulesikhatsi seliPremier League, litawuhlangana neHarts ngeLisontfo, lelibambe lichaza ku Rangers ngemaphuzu lasiphohlongo.
NgeLesine i-Rengers itawudlala umdlalo wayo we-Europe League ne-Austria Rapid (Vena).
Liveington iyachubeka nekuhlula kwayo kulelibhola letinyawo, seyibe nemidlalo lesitfupha futsi ayikaphindzi ilahlwe kusukela Holt atsatsa sikhundla saKenny Miller njengemtshayeli welicembu.
