Scott Robinson wakhona kuphuma kuloluhlaka lwekuvikela, kepha umgomo wakhe lowentiwe ngemandla lamanyenti awuzange uphumelele. Ngemuva kwaloko umvikeli Alan Lithgow, ngekushaya kakhulu, wehluleka kuvimbela ibhola yaKag Halkett kutsi ingangeni elugibeni.
