Emagundvwane bekahlala angena kuLivingston, kepha tonkhe tinchubo takhe betibanjwa, futsi timfuneko letimbili telicala - yinye yekucindzetela umdlali wesikhashana Glenn Middleton Halkett kanye nalenye yekudlala ngesandla - ayigcwalisekanga.
