Kwemukelwa lokumnandzi kwa-Erdogan ngesikhatsi avakashele eKöln
NgaLesihlanu, September 29, ngesikhatsi baholi baseTurkey nebaseJalimane bahlangana ndzawonye badla kudla kwasekuseni, bekumuhle futsi bobabili bebangenandzaba.
Bekulilanga lekugcina laMengameli Erdogan avakashele eJalimane ngenhloso yekulungisa budlelwane emkhatsini wemave lamabili langemalunga eNATO.
Baholi bemave behlulekile kutfola kucondzana ngetindzaba letifana nemalungelo eluntfu, inkhululeko yebetindzaba kanye nekungena kweTurkey e-EU.
Ngemuva kwaloko Erdogan waya eCologne kuyohlanganyela emcimbini wekusungulwa kwelithempeli lelisha lelikhulu.
Köln inebantfu labanyenti base Turkey labakhashane ne Turkey.
Ngenca yetizatfu tekuphepha, emaphoyisa awazange avumele bantfu labangu-25 000 kutsi bangene kulelisontfo, kodvwa labanyenti labasekela Erdogan batfola indzawo lesedvute kute babone umengameli wabo.
Bantfu labaphikisana nembuso wa-Erdogan, lokufaka ekhatsi emaKurd, bahlangana khona lapho kute bagcekeze inchubomgomo ya-Erdogan kanye nesincumo sahulumende waseJalimane sekummemela kutsi ete eJalimane.
Kuba khona kwemibono lephambene kulomhlangano kukhombisa kutsi lomuntfu unetimphawu letehlukene: EmaJalimane lamanyenti lanetimphandze taseTurkey amhlonipha kakhulu Erdogan, kantsi labanye bamtsatsa njengesigelekece.
Ingoti yemigwaco yaseDepthford: Kushayisana nemoto kwabulala umgibeli webhayisikili
