Umshayeli wemoto kanye netisebenti temphilo letatise kulendzawo betama kusita lomgibeli, kodvwa lomuntfu wafa angati.
Lena akusiyo kuphela ingoti leyambulala bantfu kulendzawo: Kuncenye nje yemakhilomitha kusuka lapho kwenteka khona ingoti, kuChilders Street, lomunye umgibeli wemabhayisikili washayiswa yimoto lebeyibaleka.
Emaphoyisa aseLondon atsi nyalo asebenta kute atfole kutsi ngubani lofile futsi atjele umndeni wakhe.
Kwanyalo, imigwaco ivaliwe futsi netibhasi setishintjiwe: bashayeli bayalwa kutsi bangangeni kulendzawo.
Imibhikisho ejele laseLong Lartin: Emaphoyisa lasitfupha alimele
Ngekusho kwebaphatsi baseLong Lartin, emaphoyisa lasitfupha alimala ngesikhatsi sekuhlupheka lokwenteka ejele lelisetulu lelabadvuna.
Kusukela ngeLisontfo, timphi ticale cishe nga 09:30 ngesikhatsi sasekhaya ejele lelikhulu lemadvodza laseLong Lartin, eWustershire.
Kute kuvalwe umbhikisho lofaka ekhatsi tiboshwa letisiphohlongo letiphuma esigabeni sinye, kwabitwa licembu le-Tornado.
Emaphoyisa atfole kulimala lokuncane etinhlavini letincane; atfola lusito lwetekwelapha endzaweni.
Ngekusho kwesikhulu selijele, basebenti labaceceshwe ngalokukhetsekile batfunyelwe ejele laseLong Lartin kute bacoce ngalendzaba.
Emalunga lasitfupha alomkhandlu alimele.
Siyakulahla ngalokuphelele kusetjentiswa kwemandla emtimbeni enhlanganweni yetfu, futsi kuyacaca kutsi labenti balokubi batawuniketwa emaphoyiseni futsi sigwebo sabo singashintjwa sibe sikhatsi lesidze.
I-Long Lartin nyalo inebantfu labangetulu kwa-500 labavalelwe, lokufaka ekhatsi letinye tetigebengu letiyingoti kakhulu kulelive.
NgaJuni, kwavela umbiko etincwadzini te-TV wekutsi umphatsi welijele ulele esibhedlela ngemuva kwekuhlaselwa ngulomunye walabantfu.
Nga-October emnyakeni lowengcile, baphatsi belijele baphocelelwa kutsi basebentise emabutfo labukene netindzaba letibalulekile kute bacedze kukhatsateka kwebantfu lebebaphonsa tibhola te-bilardo kubogadzi.
Rose angakhukhula i-Phoenix, iLas Vegas neSalt Lake City (lokungazuzisa tindzawo letomile)
Arizona ayivamile kuba sesimeni sezivunguvungu letinemandla, kodvwa kuloku "inhlanhla" ngobe ekucaleni kweliviki lelitako, Rose utawushaya umgwaco wakhe wekugcina endzaweni yasehlane leseNingizimu Nshonalanga futsi utawuba netingoti tekukhukhula.
I-National Weather Service seyivele icwayise ngesimo setikhukhula letinemvula ngeMsombuluko nangoLesibili enshonalanga ye-Arizona naseningizimu nasemphumalanga ye-Nevada, eningizimu-mpumalanga ye-California nase-Utah, kufaka ekhatsi emadolobha lafana ne-Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas kanye ne-Salt Lake City.
Lesimo selitulu lesibitwa ngekutsi yi-Rose, silindzelwe kutsi sifike ePhoenix ngeLesibili bese sigadla ngemvula ngeMsombuluko kusihlwa.
I-National Weather Service yasePhoenix, i-FBI, yatsi kuTwitter, kusukela nga-1950 kube netiphepho letingu-10 letatigcina tihleti tingeke tibe ngulesinye setiphepho letishisako nobe tibe ngulesinye setiphepho letishisako, letitfolakala endzaweni lengemakhilomitha langu-320 kusuka ePhoenix.
Lesiphepho i-Katrina (nga-1967) safika khashane ngemakhilomitha langu-65 kusuka e-Arizona.
Ngekusho kwe-National Meteorological Service, kutawuba nemvula lengaba ngemasentimitha lasihlanu kuya kulalishumi, bese kutsi kuletinye tindzawo ibe ngemasentimitha lasihlanu eMoglion-Rome, e-Arizona.
Kuletinye tindzawo letingenamsebenti tase Ningizimu Nshonalanga, njengase Central Rocky Mountains kanye nase Big Basin, kunemvula lengaba ngu 2.55 cm, letinye tindzawo tingaba ngu 10 cm.
Etindzaweni lapho khona imvula itawugeleta, imvula leletfwe nguRosa ingaba sibusiso ngobe lendzawo seyisikhatsi lesidze inesomiso.
Nanobe tikhukhula letinemvula tingase tibe yingoti, imvula lenkhulu ingenta kube melula kutsi kube nesomiso eNingizimu-Nshonalanga yeMelika.
Ngekusho kwemaphuzu e-U.S. Drought Monitor, cishe emaphesenti langu-40 ase-Arizona abhekene nesomiso lesikhulu (sigaba sesibili), kubika i-weather.com.
Ekucaleni, iSiphepho Rosa sitawushaya i-Lower California leseMexico.
Ngekusho kwelilanga lelisontfo ekuseni, lesiphepho, lesinesivinini lesingu 137 km/h, sitfolakala emakhilomitha lamakhulu lamatsatfu nemashumi lamatsatfu eningizimu yelidolobha lase Punta-Euchenia (eMexico) futsi siya enyakatfo ngesivinini semakhilomitha lamashumi layimfica ngelihora.
Lesiphepho sifike endzaweni lenemanti lapholile ngaselugwini lwasePacific futsi sesiphelelwa ngemandla.
Ngalesikhatsi sesihlahla lesi, lesiphepho sitawufika eMexico.
Kuletinye tindzawo taseMexico, kulindzeleke kutsi kube netimvula letinemandla letingabangela tikhukhula.
Eningizimu yeCalifornia kuya enyakatfo-nshonalanga yeSonora, kunemvula lengaba ngemasentimitha langu-710 etindzaweni letingaba ngemasentimitha langu-25, kubika i-weather.com.
Ngemuva kwaloko, iRosa itawuya enyakatfo ichubekele eMexico, bese ifika emnyeleni wase-Arizona ekuseni ngaLesibili, ibe ngulesinye setiphepho letinemandla letitawuhamba kusukela e-Arizona tiye eningizimu ye-Utah kusihlwa ngaLesibili.
Ingoti lenkhulu levela kuRosa kanye netintfo letisele, ihlobene netimvula letinkhulu e-Lower California, enyakatfo-nshonalanga yeSonora kanye nasetindzaweni tasehlane letiseNingizimu-nshonalanga yeMelika, kusho i-National Weather Service.
Lemvula leyakheke kakhulu kulindzeleke kutsi ibangele tikhukhula letinemandla, kudvuma kwetigodzi tasehlane kanye nekugedvuka kwemhlaba etindzaweni letinetintsaba.
Kuhlaselwa eMidsomer Norton: Kuboshwe bantfu labane labahloswe ngekubulala
E Somerset, umfana loneminyaka lengu-16 budzala walimala kakhulu ngemukhwa, futsi bantfwana labatsatfu kanye nemfana loneminyaka lengu-20 budzala baboshwa ngekusola kutsi bafuna kumbulala.
