Donald Trump: "Kwanobe kunjalo, i-Kavanawa yatfola lulaka, lulaka lwemaDemocrat".
"Kuvotelwa lijaji Cavanaugh" kusho kuvotelwa kuphikisana nemasu lanelunya futsi lanelulaka lasetjentiswa ngemaDemocrats", kusho Trump emhlanganweni webangani bakhe eWheeling, West Virginia.
Ngekusho kwaTrump, inchubo yekugunyaza Kvanon kutsi abe ngumuntfu lobekwe esikhundleni, yabangela kutsi kube nelulaka, nelunya lolukhulu lwelicembu lemaDemocrats.
NgaLesihlanu, Kavanaugh wafakaza e-US Congress, ngekukhuluma kwakhe lokukhombisa luvo, waphika ngalokuphelele licala laChristina Blaise Ford lekutsi wamhlukubeta ngekwelicasi eminyakeni lengetulu kwalengu-30 leyendlulile ngesikhatsi bobabili basebasha.
UDkt. Ford waphindze wafakaza ngesikhatsi sekulalelwa kwelicala lakhe.
NgaLesihlanu, Mengameli waseMelika watsi "bantfu baseMelika bakubona kuhlakanipha, liklasi kanye nesibindzi" kwaKavanaw.
"Lelivoti lekuvuma lijaji Cavanaugh" "Leli livoti lekuvuma lomunye webameli labahle kakhulu esikhatsini setfu, lonemlandvo lomuhle kakhulu wekusebenta emphakatsini", "kusho Mengameli etfule umlayeto esicukwini sebantfu labamvakashele eWest Virginia.
Kulenkhulumo yakhe, Mengameli ukhulume ngalokungakacondzakali ngekumenyelwa kwaKavanaw, akhuluma ngekubaluleka kwekuhlangana kwebavoti beRepublican kuKhomishane kanye neNdlu yeBamele.
Sekusele emaviki lasihlanu kuphela kutsi kube nelukhetfo lolubaluleke kakhulu ekuphileni kwetfu.
"Angihlanganyeli kuyo, kodvwa ngihlanganyela kulenye indlela", washo njalo.
"Ngitfwele umfutfo futsi ngivikela labo labahle kakhulu".
Trump ukholelwa kutsi emaDemocrats abeke umgomo wawo "wekutsi asiphikise ngawo onkhe emandla abo".
Ngekusho kwemitsetfomgomo, livoti lekucala lelibalulekile eSenate lekucinisekisa kutsi Cavanaugh uyavunyelwa kutsi abe ngumengameli kumele licale ngeLesihlanu, kusho umsizi wesikhulu selicembu le-Republican.
Kutamatama kwemhlaba e-Indonesia kubulale emakhulu ebantfu futsi linani lebantfu labafile liyachubeka likhula
NgaLesihlanu, tiphatsimandla tase-Indonesia tatsi bantfu labangu-384 bafile, labanyenti bashaywa ngemagagasi lamakhulu labhubhisa emabhishi esichingi sase-Indonesia i-Sulawesi, lesashaywa kutamatama kwemhlaba kanye ne-tsunami lenemandla lamakhulu.
Bantfu labakhulu lebebavakashele umkhosi waselwandle ePalu, baba ngibo labafa kwekucala, ngesikhatsi emagagasi laphakeme ngemamitha lasitfupha agubha lwandle ngaLesihlanu nakushona lilanga, futsi abulala bantfu labanyenti lebebakhona.
Kwaba ne-tsunami ngemuva kwekutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla lafinyelela ku-7.5 nge-Richter.
Lapho kutfunyelwa umlayeto wesiphepho itolo, bantfu bachubeka nekuphumula elugwini kunekutsi babalekele etindzaweni tekukhosela, futsi balahlekelwa kuphila kwabo, kusho Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, sikhulu se-Indonesia National Disaster Management Authority, enkhulumeni yelubiko eJakarta.
Kute tsunami leyake yefika, emanti abehamba ngemoto, tigodvo, tindlu, futsi konkhe lokwakusendleleni yawo kwabhidlika,  wachaza Nugraho, wachubeka watsi tsunami yewela lwandle ngelitubane lelingemakhilomitha langu-497 ngelihora futsi yahlasela lwandle ngemandla ayo onkhe.
Labanye bantfu labebalapho bagcina baphila ngekutsi bagcumagcume etihlahleni.
Bantfu labangu-16 700 basuswa etindzaweni letingu-24 ePalu.
Kuletitfombe letitsetfwe ngemoya, tindlu letibhidlitiwe, emabhuloho labhidlikile, netitolo kanye nemasontfo labekakhukhunjiswe emanti.
NgaLesihlanu, lidolobha leliselugwini belisolo litfutfumela.
Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokulandzelanako kwenteka endzaweni lenebantfu labangu-2,4 wetigidzi.
