I-USA idzinga kuphindza kabili imali yekusekela kutfutfukiswa kwe-AI
 I-USA kufanele iphindze yente imali yayo yekusungula isayensi kabili, kusho Li Kaifu, umtsengi kanye nemhwebi wetintfo tekusungula te-AI lonelwati lolunyenti ku-Google, Microsoft kanye ne-Apple.
Emahhovisi lamanyenti aseMelika abeke amemetela kutsi asebenta nge-AI, nanobe i-USA ingenawo umgomo locacile wekutfutfukisa i-AI.
Ngesikhatsi lesifanako, iChina yetfula luhlelo lwayo lwangemnyaka lophelile: Inhloso yayo kuba ngulokucala ekuguculeni i-AI nga-2030.
Kwenyusa imali yekucwaninga nge-AI kabili kungaba sicalo lesihle, uma ucabanga kutsi onkhe lamanye emave asemuva kakhulu kune-USA, futsi silindzele kuphumelela lokulandzelako kwe-AI,  kusho Lee.
Kukhokha imali lephindvwe kabili kungenta kube matima kutsi intfutfuko lelandzelako ye-AI yentiwe eMelika, Lee washo njalo kulenkhulumo yakhe ne-CNBC kuleliviki.
Li, lonencwadzi letsi "Superpowers of Artificial Intelligence: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" leyaphrintwa kulenyanga yi-Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, ungumphatsi lomkhulu we Sinovation Ventures, lebeyitsenge kulenye yetinkampani letiphambili te-AI eChina, i-Face ++.
Ngemnyaka wa 1980 e-University yase Carnegie Mellon, wasebenta eluhlelweni lwebuhlakani lobuciko lobuciko lobuciko lobucinile lobudlula lobudlalwa ngu-Othello waseMelika, wase uba ngumholi we-Microsoft Research kanye nemengameli we-Google yase China.
Li wakhuluma ngemiklomelo yetekuhweba yahulumende waseMelika, njengemncintiswano we-Defense Advanced Research Projects' Robotics Challenge, wabuta kutsi utawuba khona nini lomncintiswano lolandzelako kute asite ekutfoleni bantfu labanemibono lengakavami.
Li utsi bacwaningi baseMelika bavame kusebenta kamatima kute batfole imali yahulumende.
Li uyaciniseka kutsi akusibo baholi betemfundvo labatsatfwa yiChina, kepha tinkapani.
Facebook, iGoogle kanye naletinye tinkampani tebucwepheshe ticashe bantfu labanemandla labasemanyuvesi kutsi basebente ekuhlakanipheni lokute emakhono eminyakeni lembalwa leyengcile.
Li uyaciniseka kutsi kugucula inchubomgomo yekungena eveni kungasita iMelika kutsi itfutfukise kuhlakanipha lokute emakhono.
"Ngicabanga kutsi emakhadi laluhlata kumele aniketwe bantfu labafuna umsebenti wekusebenta ngebuhlakani lobungoti", kusho yena.
NgaJuly 2017, Umkhandlu Wesive waseShayina wakhipha luhlelo lwekutfutfukisa luhlelo lolulandzelako lwekuhlakanipha.
Li utsi, i-National Science Foundation yaseChina iniketa bososayensi imali lefanako naleyo i-National Science Foundation kanye naletinye tinhlangano tahulumende letinika bacwaningi baseMelika imali, kodvwa lizinga lemsebenti wesayensi eChina liphansi.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, Litiko Letekuvikela laseMelika lasungula i-Joint Artificial Intelligence Center, lekumele ibandzakanyiswe ngulabo labasebenta nayo etinhlelweni tetimboni netetesayensi, kantsi i-White House yamemetela kusungulwa kweKomidi Lekhetsekile ye-AI.
Kulenyanga, i-DARPA imemetele kutsi itawutsatsa imali lengemadola latigidzigidzi letimbili kuloluhlelo lolubitwa ngekutsi yi-AI Next.
I-NSF nyalo seyisebentisa tigidzi temadola letingu-100 ngemnyaka ekucwaningeni nge-AI.
Ngesikhatsi lesifanako, umtsetfo waseMelika lofuna kwakhiwa kweKhomishini Yekuphepha Kwavelonkhe ye-AI, awukenti lutfo tinyanga letinyenti.
