Satiso semhlangano weNottingham East Labor Assembly ngeLesihlanu satsi sifuna kutsi umhlangano ube ngulobunako futsi ube nemiphumela lemihle.
Sikhatsi lesinyenti seminyaka lesiphohlongo ngisebenta njengelilunga lephalamende le-Labour Party, imihlangano ye-GC yangeLesihlanu kusihlwa beyifana nalena.
Ngalokubuhlungu, indlela lamuhla lesetjentiswe ngayo ayihambisani naleminye imihlangano, kantsi nesetsembiso setfu senchubomgomo lenemusa nalenenhlonipho sesikhishiwe, uma ngabe sake saba njalo.
Loku kubonakala kakhulu kutsi licembu le-Labour alisavumi kwehlukahlukana, futsi umbono ngamunye ubukwa ngekutsi uyafaneleka yini kubaphatsi belicembu.
Loku kwacala ngemuva nje kwekutsi Jeremy abe ngumholi, ngesikhatsi bangani bami, lebengikadze ngibona imibono yabo yetembusave ifana neyakhe, bacala kulindzela kutsi ngishintje umbono wami futsi ngitsatse tincumo lebengingeke ngivumelane nato - kungaba tindzaba tekuphepha kwesive nobe temakethe lehlangene ye-EU.
Ngaso sonkhe sikhatsi nangenta inkhulumo yami - kungakhatsalekile kutsi ngitsini - kuletinye tinhlelo tekuchumana, kuvele kuhlatjwe ngetihlamba, kubitwa kutsi kukhetfwe bantfu labangeke basemkhatsini, kulahlwe tinchubomgomo telikhetselo, nobe kutsi angifanele kuba lilunga lelicembu le-Labour.
