Kusukela ngajoyina licembu le-Labor eminyakeni lengu-32 leyengcile, ngisemncane esikolweni, ngikhatsatwa yindlela hulumende waThatcher labekabukela phansi ngayo, lokwacedza liklasi lami, bengifuna kuvikela lizinga lelisetulu lemisebenti yahulumende kulabo labayidzinga kakhulu - kungaba ngumsebenti welilunga lephalamende nobe umfundisi wahulumende.
