Ngekusho kwemiphumela yekuhlola yekugcina yalomnyaka, sibona kutsi tilwimi tihola emagameni etinhlaka temidlalo futsi tinemaphuzu lasetulu ekuhlolwa etikolweni letitimele.
Bonkhe bafundzi labangu-68% labafundza tilwimi bangenisa ticu letingu-A.
Lemininingwane leyatfolwa etikolweni letingu-74 letingumalunga e-SCIS, yakhombisa kutsi bafundzi labangu-72% batfole A ngesiMandarin (sichazamagama sesiShayina), kantsi 72% labafundza siJalimane, 69% labafundza siFulentji, kanye na-63% labafundza siSpanish nabo batfole A.
Loku kukhombisa kutsi etikolweni letitimele taseScotland tilwimi tangaphandle tibonakala tibalulekile kubantfwana nakubantfu labasha esikhatsini lesitako.
Nyalo tifundvo telulwimi tifunwa njengaletitifundvo tesayensi, tebuchwepheshe, tebucwepheshe netibalo etikolweni letitimele nakuletinye tikhungo temfundvo.
Lucwaningo lolwentiwe yi-Employment and Skills Commission yase-UK nga-2014 lwaveta kutsi 17 ekhulwini walobunye lobubangela kutsi bacashi bakutfole kumatima kugcwalisa tikhala temisebenti kutsi bantfu labete emakhono elulwimi.
Ngako-ke, emakhono elulwimi aya ngekuba sisekelo sekuba nemsebenti lophumelelako.
Njengobe imisebenti lemikhulu idzinga lwati lwetilwimi, lamakhono ayadzingeka kulelive leligcwele kutfutfuka kwemhlaba.
Kungakhatsaliseki kutsi umfundzi ukhetsa muphi umsebenti, uma afundza lulwimi lwesibili, utawutfola inzuzo lenkhulu esikhatsini lesitako ngekutfola likhono lelitsite lelitawusita imphilo yakhe yonkhe.
Kuba nelikhono lekuchumana nebantfu labachamuka kulamanye emave ngekucophelela kunika umuntfu lowati tilwimi letinyenti inzuzo.
