Kungako kutsenga imali ekufundzeni tilwimi kubaluleke kangaka nyalo.
Kwati tilwimi letinyenti, ikakhulukati tilwimi temave latfutfukako, kutawenta bantfwana batfole umsebenti lokahle.
Etikolweni taseScotland kunekungafani lokukhulu mayelana netilwimi letifundziswa etikolweni.
Letinye tikolwa tifundzisa tilwimi letisemtsetfweni, kantsi letinye tifundzisa tilwimi letibonakala tibalulekile eNgilandi kute kube ngu-2020  njengesiMandarin nesiJapane.
Nobe ngabe ngumiphi imikhuba yemntfwana wakho, tikolwa letitimele titawuchubeka tikhetse tilwimi letinyenti, tifundziswe bafundzi labati kahle tilwimi.
Tikolwa letitimele taseScotland tifuna kwakha simondzawo sekufundza lesitawenta bantfwana bakulungele futsi sibahlomise ngemakhono labadzingekako kute baphumelele, nome ngabe likusasa labo litawuba njani.
