Kulindzele kubukela LeBron James adlala kwekucala e-Los Angeles Lakers sekuphelile.
Umceceshi weLakers, Luke Walton, umemetele kutsi James utawudlala umdlalo wangaphambi kwesikhatsi weLisontfo ne Denver Nuggets eSan Diego.
Kodvwa sisengakwati kutsi utawutsatsa sikhatsi lesingakanani kute aphindze atfole imali.
"Kunyenti kunaloko lokunye futsi kuncane kunangemashumi lamane nesiphohlongo", kusho Walton ku-website ye-Lakers.
Mike Trudell, lobekabika ngeLakers, wabhala kuTwitter kutsi James utawudlala sikhatsi lesincane.
Ngemuva kwekuceceshwa ekucaleni kwaleliviki, James wabutwa ngemalungiselelo akhe emidlalo lesitfupha yasekwindlalekweni ye-Lakers.
"Kulesigaba semsebenti wami, angidzingi imidlalo yangaphambi kwesikhatsi sekudlala kute ngilungele umnyaka", kuphendvula lomdlali.
Umncintiswano waTrump eWest Virginia, ku-YouTube
Mengameli Donald Trump utawucala umhlangano wekukhetsa lomusha kusihlwa eWheeling, eVirginia leseNshonalanga.
Loku kungukubona kwekucala kwetihlangano letisihlanu taTrump letihlelelwe liviki lelitako, kufaka ekhatsi kuvakashela emave aseTennessee naseMississippi.
Njengobe kuvota ngekumiswa kwakhe njengejaji lelikhulu sekubekelwe eceleni, Trump ufuna kutfola lusito elukhetfweni lolusemkhatsini, ngobe emaRepublican angahle alahlekelwe kulawula iCongress uma kuvota kwenteka ngaNovemba.
Ngusiphi sikhatsi lesitawuba khona kulomhlangano waTrump eWest Virginia kusihlwa futsi ungawubukela njani ku-inthanethi?
Umhlangano naTrump eWheeling, West Virginia, utawuba ngu-7:00 ntsambama ngesikhatsi saseMpumalanga lamuhla, uMgcibelo, Septhemba 29, 2018.
Ungakubuka kuhlangana kwaTrump nebakhi baseWest Virginia ku-intanethi ngekusakaza bukhoma ku-YouTube.
Trump kungenteka kutsi utawukhuluma kuleliviki mayelana nekubeka Brett Kavanaugh esikhundleni seNkantolo lePhakeme, lokuyintfo lebeyingajabulisi kakhulu ngobe Kavanaugh bekabekwe emacala ekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicasi, futsi kuvotelwa lokube sekufanele kwentiwe eSenate kutawuncishiswa kuze kube liviki linye ngesikhatsi i-FBI icwaninga.
Kodvwa injongo lenkhulu yalomkhankhaso kusita bantfu labafuna kuba ngemalunga e-Republican latawukhetfwa ngaNovemba kutsi batfutfukise indlela yabo yekukhetsa.
Ngako-ke, umkhankaso waMengameli Trump uhlose kutsi imihlangano lesihlanu letawuba khona kuleliviki lelitako, isite kuvuselela emavolontiya kanye nebasekeli, njengobe emaRephabliki etama kuvikela nekukhulisa linyenti lawo eSenate naseNdlini yeBamele, kusho iReuters.
"Kulawula iCongress kubaluleke kakhulu eluhlelweni lwakhe, kutsi Mengameli kumele avakashele emave lamanyenti njengobe singena esikhatsini sekukhangisa", kusho sikhulumi semkhankhaso waTrump, lowala kubitwa ngeligama, kubika iReuters.
Umcimbi lohlelwe lamuhla eWesbanco Arena eWheeling, ungahle uletse bantfu labasuka e-Ohio nasePennsylvania, futsi ubambe babhali betindzaba basePittsburgh, kubika i-West Virginia Metro News.
Kuvakasha kwaTrump eWest Virginia ngaMgcibelo  kungukuhambela kwesibili kulelive enyangeni leyendlulile, ngobe ngulapho atfole khona emaphesenti langetulu kwa-40 ekuhola nga-2016.
Trump wetama kusita Patrick Morrissey, lofuna kuba ngumengameli waseWestern Virginia, lowehluleka kakhulu.
Kutsi uMorrisy afanele abe ngumengameli kute acale kuba ngetulu kwalabanye bantfu kutemaphenyo  akusiso sibonakaliso lesihle kuMorrisy,  kusho Simon Heather, losati setembusave eNyuvesi yase West Virginia (locashunwe yi Reuters).
Ryder Cup 2018: I-USA ikhombisa kutimisela nekubukana nekubukana, iya emncintiswaneni webantfu lababili ngeLisontfo
Ngemuva kwekubukana tikhatsi letintsatfu, umdlalo waMgcibelo, 2-2 mhlawumbe nguloko kanye lokwakudzingwa yiRyder Cup.
Lelisu lekucala  liyincenye yemidlalo leyakhiwe, kodvwa ngulapho badlali bakholelwa khona futsi libonakala kakhulu kulemidlalo.
Ngubani lona lowenta loku?
"Bebanemaphuzu lasitfupha ekudlala, nyalo sebasemaphuzwini lamane, ngako-ke ngicabanga kutsi loku kuyintfo lencane kitsi", kusho Jordan Speeth ashiya.
Yebo, iYurophu inemaphuzu lamane ekuhola, kantsi kusasele langu-12 kutsi ibe khona.
Ngekusho kwaSpith, bantfu baseMelika "banemoya lomuhle" futsi banetizatfu tekuhlala badzangele, lokufaka ekhatsi indlela yabo yekudlala, Spit naJustin Thomas badlala ndzawonye lilanga lonkhe, futsi ngamunye wabo utfole emaphuzu lamatsatfu kulamane.
Kulala kwakhe bekungasuki etulu, kunaloko bekangikhombisa.
Imphimbo yekuncoba yagcwala kakhulu njengobe umjikeni wakhe uchubeka, wafaka ibhola lebalulekile emgodzini, wavala umdlalo ngesikhatsi yena naThomas sebalahlekile nga-2-2.
Umgamu wakhe lowabashaya nga-15 wahlangana nemsindvo lofanako, lokusho kukholwa kwakhe kutsi liTiko laseMelika lingakhona.
"Kufanele sihlangane sonkhe futsi sinake umdlalo wetfu", kusho Spit.
Loku ngiko kuphela lokusele kubadlali.
Kwenta ema-hole langu-18 bese uyaphumelela.
Ngulabadlali labodvwa labazuze emaphuzu lamanyenti kuletikhatsi letimbili letengcile kunaSpite naThomas, nguFrancesco Molinari naTommy Fleetwood, labafaka umlandvo weRyder Cup.
Labashadikazi lababili labatsandzekako baseYurophu batfole emaphutsa lamane, futsi kubonakala shengatsi abati kutsi yini lengakalungi.
I-Mollywood ngiyo kuphela indvodza nemfati lebebangayi kubamba umntfwana ngensimbi yeMgcibelo, kodvwa baphindze bayigwema intsambama, ngeLesihlanu, nangakusasa futsi.
Loluchungechunge kanye nendlela emandla abo labonakala ajikeleta ngayo emkhatsini wabo kanye netibukeli letiphitsitelako, kucinisa kukholwa kwabo kutsi ngeLisontfo batawuphindze bangaphumeleli futsi ngesikhatsi lilanga lishona ngemuva kweLe Golf National, kute umdlali lotawubonakala kakhulu lotawubamba umchudzelwano waseYurophu kunaFleetwood nobe Molinari.
Bekutawuba kuhle kutsi bobabili babe semgodzini lohlukile ngesikhatsi lesifanako.
Kodvwa kusengakatfwasi kutsi sikhulume ngebuhle beYurophu.
BoBubba Watson naWebbe Simpson basheshe babulala Sergio Garcia, umlingisi lomkhulu welibhola letine ekuseni ngesikhatsi ahlangana na-Alex Noren.
Emagugu kanye nalamanye lamabili lamakhulu, emaceleni ekucala layimfica, agubha umgodzi wase Spain kanye ne Sweden, futsi abazange baphindze bakhone kuphuma kuwo.
Ngako kute umuntfu lotakusita kutsi uphume kulomgodzi ngeLisontfo.
Kujabulisa kakhulu kubukela imidlalo yema-four-ball kanye ne-four-ball ngenca yekusebentisana emkhatsini webadlali lababili, ngeteluleko labatishintsanako kodvwa labatigodlako, nekutsi indlela yekudlala ingashintja njani ngekushesha.
Kuze kube ngunyalo, iYurophu beyisebenta kahle njengelicembu futsi beyikhuphuka kakhulu ngelilanga lekugcina, kepha lomhlangano wema-4 uphindze wakhombisa kutsi licembu laseMelika linemandla ekubhekana nalobumatima labanye bantfu, ikakhulukati eMelika, lebebacabanga kutsi angeke bakhone kubhekana nabo.
Ngelilanga lekugcina le-Ryder Cup, i-Europe ihola nga-10-6
I-Europe itawutfola umncono wekugcina ngelilanga lekugcina le-Ryder Cup ngemuva kwekuphela kwemidlalo yemidlalo lemine neyesine ngeMgcibelo, ibe ne-10-6 kunemave aseMelika.
Umlingani lohloniphekile Tommy Fleetwood na Francesco Molinari bahola umzabalazo ngekuncoba kabili Tiger Woods lowalwa, kwentela kuletsa inombolo ku Le Golf National ibe ngemaphuzu lamane.
Licembu laseYurophu laThomas Bjorn, lelifuna kubuyisela indondo lebeliyicitse eHazeltine eminyakeni lemibili leyengcile, lahola licembu laseMelika lebeliphutsa emidlalweni yasekuseni yemabhola lamane, lancoba nga-3-1.
I-USA yafaka umfutfo lomkhulu kuma-four, incobe imidlalo lemibili, kepha ayizange ikhone kunciphisa umehluko.
Licembu laJim Ferrick lidzinga emaphoyinti lasiphohlongo emidlalweni lengu-12 ngeLisontfo kute lihlale liyincenye yelive.
Fleetwood ngumdlali wekucala wase Europe lowatfola emaphoyinti lamane lalandzelanako, kantsi yena naMolinairi, labetfole ligama lelitsi Mollywood ngemuva kwekuphela kwempelasonto, baba yincenye yesibili yebantfu lababili labatfole emaphoyinti lamane emidlalweni yabo lemine yekucala emlandvweni we Ryder Cup.
Ngemuva kwekuncoba Woods naPatrick Reed ngemabhola lamane, bahlangana ngekuhlangana kute bancobe Woods lobekafile kanye naBrison DeChebmo waseMelika lobekacala kufundza ngekuncoba nga-5/4.
Woods, lowadlala imidlalo lemibili ngaMgcibelo, bekakhombisa kutsi ushaywa ngemandla, kodvwa nyalo ulahlekelwe yimidlalo lengu-19 kulabangu-29 ngemagoli lamane, futsi ema-four acala kusebenta kasikhombisa.
Justin Rose, lowakhutsateka ngaphambi kwemdlalo wasekuseni wemabhola lamane, wabuyela kumlingani wakhe Henrik Stenson kumdlalo wesine, wancoba Dustin Johnson na Brooks Keppka nga 2/1, labatiholako kulesitsatfu kanye nakulesibili emhlabeni.
EYurophu, lomdlalo awuzange ube lula futsi awuzange ube luhambo lolumnandzi loluhamba emini lephumulako eningizimu-nshonalanga yeParis.
Emaphuzu lamabili lazuzwe ngunyalo nguJordan Spit naJustin Thomas, lababe ngumshicileli wemidlalo yetemidlalo emahlandla lamatsatfu, aba yintfo lebalulekile kubantfu baseMelika.
Bawina ngekuncintisana nga 2/1 ku John Ram na Ian Polter base Spain emdlalweni wemabhola lamane futsi babuya emuva kwesikhatsi kute bancobe Polter na Rory McIlroy nga 4/3 kumane, balahlekelwa yimigodzi lemibili yekucala.
Kwekugcina, emacembu lamabili kuphela emlandvweni we Ryder Cup laphuma embili ngemaphuzu lamane, aphuma yedvwa, ngekubuka kutsi licembu laFerik, njengebasebenti, bekufanele lidlale ngekubumbana kute ligcine umklomelo.
Nanobe kunjalo, ngemuva kwemalanga lamabili bahola, kulwa kwabo ngeLisontfo kubonakala shengatsi sekwendlulele.
INyakatfo Korea itsi angeke ihlasele ngalokungakhetsi ngaphandle kwekwetsembana
INdvuna yeTangaphandle yaseNyakatfo Korea itjele iNhlangano yaMhlabuhlangene ngeMgcibelo kutsi kuvinjelwa lokuchubekako kucinisa kungetsembi iMelika nekutsi kute simo lapho live layo lingeke lilahle khona tikhali talo te-nuclear ngendlela yinye.
Ri Yong Ho, lowatisa umhlangano wemnyaka we-General Assembly, watsi i-North Korea yente "tinyatselo letibalulekile telutsandvo" emnyakeni lowengcile, njengekumisa kuhlolwa kwenyukliya kanye nemakhemikhali, kucedza indzawo yayo yekusebentisa inyukliya, kanye nekungatihlanganisi netintfo letitsite letitsite.
"Noko, asikaboni kutsi iMelika iphendvule ngendlela lefana naleyo", washo njalo.
"Kute litsemba nge-United States lelitawuba nekuciniseka ngekuphepha kwetfu, futsi angeke sikhone kwenta umsebenti wekucala wekulwa nekuhlukunyetwa kwetimphi".
Nanobe Ri aphindze akhuluma ngekukhalata kwe North Korea ngekungafuni kwe Washington kutsi kube ne "sikhatsi" sekucedza i-denuclearization, lapho khona i-North Korea itawuvuzwa ngetinyatselo letincane, lesitatimende sakhe sabonakala sibalulekile ngobe asizange sikulahle kucedvwa kwe-denuclearization ngalokungenamcondziso, njengobe i-Pyongyang yente esikhatsini lesengcile.
Ri wacaphuna sitatimende lesihlangene lesentiwa nguKim Jong-un naDonald Trump emhlanganweni wekucala emkhatsini wemengameli waseMelika kanye nemholi waseNyakatfo Korea lowabanjelwa eSingapore ngaJuni 12; ngaleso sikhatsi Kim wetsembisa kucala kuhamba ngendlela yekulwa ne-nuclear e-Korean Peninsula, kantsi Trump wetsembisa i-North Korea kutsi itawuba nekuphepha.
INyakatfo Korea ifuna kucedza imphi yase Korea yanga 1950-53, kepha iUnited States itsi i-Pyongyang kumele icale ilahle tikhali tayo te-nuclear.
I-Washington iphindze imelane neticelo tekwehlisa kucindzetelwa lokumatima kwe-North Korea.
iMelika igcizelela kutsi kufanele kube nekucitfwa kwembutfo wenyukliya kucala, futsi ikhulisa lizinga lekucindzetela ngekusebentisa tinhlawulo kute ifinyelele umgomo wayo futsi iphindze iphikisane nekumenyetelwa kwekuphela kwemphi,  kusho Ri.
"Umcabango wekutsi kujeziswa kungasibeka ematseni" "liphupho lelingeke liphumelele lebantfu labangasiboni".
Kodvwa inkinga mbamba kutsi kucindzeteleka lokuchubekako kucinisa kungetsembi kwetfu.
Ri akazange akhulume ngeluhlelo lwekuhlangana kwesibili kwaKim naTrump, lokuchazwe ngumholi waseMelika e-United Nations ekucaleni kwaleliviki.
Esikhundleni saloko, lomengameli wagcizelela imihlangano lemitsatfu emkhatsini waKim neMholi waseNingizimu Korea, Moon Jae-in, letenteke etinyangeni letisihlanu letengcile, futsi wachubeka watsi: Kube lelicala lekucedza tibhuce belingaba seNingizimu Korea, hhayi eMelika, lokucedza tibhuce eNhlonhlweni yaseKorea bekungeke kube yintfo lephutfumako.
Nanobe kunjalo, indlela Ri lakhuluma ngayo beyehluke kakhulu kunaloko lakusho emnyakeni lowengcile ngesikhatsi etjela Umhlangano Wetive Letihlangene kutsi kuhlasela kweNyakatfo Korea emaveni aseMelika bekungeke kuphele ngemuva kwekutsi Mengameli Trump abite Kim ngekutsi ngumuntfu lohlasela ngekutibulala.
Kulomnyaka e-UN, Trump, lowesabise 'kubhubhisa' iNyakatfo Korea emnyakeni lowengcile, wadvumisa Kim ngesibindzi sakhe sekwenta tinyatselo tekulwa nekuhlukunyetwa, kepha watsi kunyenti lokusamele kwentiwe futsi kuvinjelwa kumele kuhlale kusebenta kuze kube ngulapho iNyakatfo Korea ihlukunyetwa.
NgaLwesitsatfu, Trump watsi akazange abeke sikhatsi lesitsite saloluhlelo: "Kungakhatsaleki kutsi kutsatsa iminyaka lemibili, iminyaka lemitsatfu nobe tinyanga letisihlanu".
I-China neRussia bacabanga kutsi uMkhandlu weTekuphepha we-UN kumele ukhutsate iPyongyang ngetinyatselo letitsetfwe.
Nanobe kunjalo, Ndvunankhulu weMbuso waseMelika Mike Pompeo, watsi eMkhandlwini weTekuphepha we-UN ngeLesine: "Kufaka tigwebo eMkhandlwini weTekuphepha kumele kuchubeke ngekutimisela futsi ngendlela ledzingekile size sibone kuvalwa kwembutfo wenyukliya lokuphelele, lokugcwele futsi lokucinisekisiwe".
Kusukela nga-2006, uMkhandlu Wetekuphepha wavumelana ngekucinisa kujeziswa kweNyakatfo Korea, wetama kuvala imali ye-Pyongyang yetinhlelo tayo te-nuclear kanye netemakhemikhali.
Pompeo wahlangana naRi ngemuva kweNgcungcutsela ye-UN General Assembly, futsi ngemuva kwalengcungcutsela watjela kutsi utawuvakashela iPhenyang futsi ngenyanga letako kute alungiselele umhlangano wesibili.
Pompeo uvakashele eNyakatfo Korea katsatfu kulomnyaka, kodvwa luhambo lwakhe lwekugcina aluphumelelanga.
NgaJulayi, washiya iPhenyang, atsi kukhona lokuchubekako, kepha emahoreni lambalwa ngemuva kwaloluhambo, iNorth Korea yamlahla ngekumfuna kutsi ente tintfo tebugebengu.
INyakatfo Korea yetsembise emhlanganweni lobanjwe ngu Moon kulenyanga kutsi itawucedza luhlelo lwayo lwekuhambisa tindiza kanye neluhlelo lwekuhambisa inyukliya uma ngabe iMelika itsatsa tinyatselo letifanele.
Ngekusho kwakhe, Kim wamtjela kutsi "tinyatselo letifanele" labekhuluma ngato, "tintfo tekuvikela kuphepha letetsenjiswa nguTrump eSingapore, kanye netento leticondziswe ekuvuseleleni budlelwane neWashington".
Bafundzi baseHarvard bafundza kutfokotela tifundvo letibalulekile
Kantsi futsi, indlela lensha leyentiwa eHarvard University kulomnyaka, yenta kutsi bonkhe bafundzi labaseminyakeni yekucala bafundze kulala sikhatsi lesinyenti futsi balwisane nemasiko ekudzakwa kwe-caffeine kute bahlale baphapheme ebusuku.
Lomunye umfundzi utfole kutsi bafundzi labaphumelela kakhulu emhlabeni bavame kungacabangi kutsi kufanele batinakekele njani.
Charles Chesler, longuprofesa wetekwelapha ngekulala eHarvard Medical School futsi lofaka sandla eBrigham and Women's Hospital, usungule indlela lacabanga kutsi ngiyo yekucala eMelika.
Ngemuva kwekutfola kutsi kunjani, wacala kufundzisa ngekulala kahle, futsi wacala ngekubhala inkhulumo ngemiphumela yekungalali kahle ekufundzeni.
Ngasekupheleni kwalenkhulumo yami, intfombatana yeta kimi yatsi: 'Ngifisa sengatsi ngabe bengingatati letindzaba nyalo, njengobe sengicedza esikolweni.'
Watsi kute umuntfu lowake wamtjela ngekubaluleka kwekulala - lokwangimangalisa - washo njalo kuThe Telegraph.
Lenkhosi, letawucala kufundvwa bafundzi kulomnyaka, ikhuluma ngekutsi indlela yekulala kahle ingasita njani ekufundzeni nasekutfutfukiseni temidlalo, kanye nekutsi ingakwenta njani umuntfu ative ancono.
Paul Barrera, longuphrofesa wetemphilo yengcondvo eHarvard Medical School futsi longumcondzisi lophetse we-University Health Services, utsi leNyuvesi yenta sincumo sekusungula loluhlelo ngemuva kwekubona kutsi bafundzi bebabete butfongo lobanele ngesikhatsi semnyaka.
Sifundvo sitsatsa li-awa linye, bafundzi benta imisebenti lehlukahlukene.
Kulenye incenye, bafundzi bafundza ngekucaphuna tinkomishi temakhofi, emakhethini, tintfo tekufundza kanye netincwadzi kute batfole lwati ngekutsi tintfo letimbalwa - ikhofi, kukhanya, nekungalali kahle - tiyilimata njani indlela bantfu labativocavoca ngayo kanye nekutsi kubaluleke kangakanani kulala ngalokwenele onkhe malanga.
Kulenye incenye, bafundzi batawufundza ngekutsi kungalali sikhatsi lesidze kungakhulisa bungoti bekuhlaselwa sifo senhlitiyo, sifo sekushaya unyawo, kucindzeteleka kanye nemdlavuza.
Lemephu yekusebenta yesikhungo ikhutsata bafundzi kutsi bacabange ngemphilo yabo yemalanga onkhe.
Siyacaphela kutsi lemfundvo angeke igucule kutiphatsa kwebafundzi ngekushesha.
Kodvwa sicabanga kutsi banelilungelo lekufundza, njengabo bonkhe bantfu, kutsi kubhema kuyitsintsa njani imphilo yabo", kwengeta Phrofesa Chesler.
Utsi, "Lokutigabatisa ngekungalali busuku bonkhe kusasakatekile, futsi buchwepheshe kanye nekucindzetelwa kwebafundzi kutsi balale, kusho kutsi kunenkinga".
Utsi, kulala lokwenele lokunemphilo "kuyisikhali lesiyimfihlo" semfundzi sekulwa nekucindzeteleka, kukhatsateka kanye nekukhatsateka, ngisho nekulwa nekukhuluphala, ngobe kungalali kahle kwenta ingcondvo ingalali kahle, futsi loko kwenta umfundzi ahlale alambile.
Raymond Saw, umfana loneminyaka lengu-19 budzala waseCalifornia lofundza ngekwakheka kwemvelo kanye nekwakheka kwemvelo, wasita Phrofesa Chesler kutsi akhe sifundvo ngekutsi aye esifundvweni sakhe semnyaka lowengcile ngesikhatsi afundza eHarvard.
Watsi lesifundvo samvula emehlo futsi samkhutsata kutsi ashumayele ngalendzaba kulo lonkhe likhampasi.
Ufuna kutsi bonkhe bafundzi labaphotfule tifundvo tabo te-bachelor bafundze luhlelo lolufanako ngaphambi kwekutsi bangene esikolweni.
Phrofesa Chesler utjela bafundzi kutsi bafake ema-alamu labakhutsata kutsi balale futsi bavuke, baphindze bakhumbule kutsi kukhanya lokuluhlata sasibhakabhaka lokukhishwa tikrini te-elekthroniki netibane te-LED kuyayiphatamisa indlela umuntfu lalala ngayo futsi kungabangela kutsi kube matima kulala.
 Livingston 1 - 0  Rangers: Inhloso yaMeng iletsa kuncoba ecenjini laGerrard
"Bafana ne Rangers" baphindze babhekana nalenye inhlupheko yekuphuma njengoba inhloso yaDolly Meng yaholela ecenjini lelingakahlanganiswa laSteven Gerrard ekuhlushweni ngu-1-0 eLivingston.
Licembu la-Aibrox belinembono wekuphumelela kwekucala ekhaya ngemuva kwekuncoba nga-4-1 ngaFebruwari eSt Johnstone, kepha licembu laGary Holt lamehlisa Gerrard emidlalweni lengu-18 njengengameli, lashiya licembu lakhe linemaphuzu lasiphohlongo ngemuva, lincoba kancane i-Hearts, licembu lelibusa eScotland Premier League.
Manga wafaka umgomo ngemizuzu lesikhombisa ngaphambi kwekuphumula, kantsi licembu lema Rangers, lebeliphelelwe ngemandla, alizange lifune kulinganisa.
Ngesikhatsi i Rangers seyihlele endzaweni yesitfupha, i Livingston seyivele seyifikile endzaweni yesitsatfu, futsi seyihlelwe yi Hibernian kuphela ngekuhlanganiswa kwemagoli.
Ema Rangers angahle abe netinkinga letengetiwe ngemuva kwekutsi umphatsi weligatja Calum Spence aphilise inxeba lakhe enhloko ngemuva kwekulahlwa kwentsambo letsite esigabeni sebantfu labavakashile.
Gerrard wente kubamba lichaza kwayisishiyagalombili kulelicembu lelihamba nge-Er kuya kumdlalo wekugcina we-Scottish League Cup.
Holt naye wenta ngendlela lefanako naleyo lebeyentiwa nguLeevi 11 ngesikhatsi ahlukanisa na-Hearts ngeliviki leliphelile, futsi bekatawujabula kubona kutsi labantfu labatsite labatsite bebabancane.
