Almanac: Umsunguli we Geiger counter
Nyalo sekusekhasini le-almanac yetfu, "Elingakusasa ekuseni": NgeLesihlanu ekuseni ngaSeptemba 30, 1882, eminyakeni lengu-136 leyendlulile, ngalelolanga, kutalwa Johannes Wilhelm Hans Geiger, lobekatawuba ngusomabhayisikobho eJalimane.
Geiger wasungula indlela yekubona nekulinganisa umsakazo, lokusungula lokwagcina kuholele ekwakhiweni kwendlela leyatiwa ngekutsi yi Geiger counter.
Njengobe sekuba yintfo lesisekelo sesayensi, i-Gayger counter yaba yintfo lesisekelo semasiko latsandvwa kakhulu, futsi loku kwabonakala ku-movie yemnyaka wa-1950 i-Coronado Bell, naRoy Rogers naDale Evans labatibona bangema-cowboy, labangafani netati, labadlala indzima lenkhulu:
Indvodza: "Yini lena?"
Rogers: Lena ngumsimeto we Geiger, losetjentiswa kutfola tintfo letinemandla emsakazo njenge uranium.
Uma ugcoka lama-headphone, ungaweva emandla ema-athomu lavela ngekusebenta kwemandla emvelo kumaminerali.
Ngulapho-ke lapho ngilalela khona!
Hans Geiger wafa nga-1945, asesele emalanga lambalwa kutsi agcwalise iminyaka lengu-63.
Kodvwa intfo yakhe, lebitwa ngemuntfu lowayibhala, isasetjentiswa kakhulu.
Umutsi lomusha wekugoma umdlavuza ungafundzisa umtimba wakho kutsi ubone emangcoliso
Umjovo lomusha wekulapha umdlavuza ungafundzisa umtimba wakho kutsi ubone emangcoliso lavelako futsi uwabulale
Incenye yekwelapha kwemjovo kutsi ufundzise umtimba wakho kutsi ubone emangcoliso
Lendlela ikhomba kutsatsa emaseli emtimba emuntfu logulako bese uyashintja endzaweni yekusebentela
Loku kwenta kutsi emangqamuzana akwati kubona tinhlobo letinyenti temdlavuza, bese ayalwa kutsi aphindze abe khona.
Lomutsi wetekuvikela sifo sewukhombise imiphumela lemihle etigulini letinetinhlobo letehlukene temdlavuza.
Kulomunye umuntfu logulako lowatfola lomjovo futsi loluhlelo lwakhe lwekulwa nekugula lwafundza kubona emangcoliso, umdlavuza wema-ovari sewuyehla tinyanga letingu-18.
Lendlela itsatsa emaseli emtimba emuntfu futsi ayashintja endzaweni yekusebentela, bese lamaseli laguculwe angabona i-HER2 protein, lekhona etinhlotjeni letinyenti temdlavuza, bese lamaseli laguculwe abuyiselwa kumuntfu.
Phrofesa Jay Berzofsky, wase-U.S. National Cancer Institute, eBethesda, Maryland utsi: "Loku lesikutfolile kukhombisa kutsi sesitfole umutsi wekugoma lonemandla".
Profesa Berzofsky uyachaza: "I-HER2 ivuselela kukhula kwetinhlobo letinyenti temdlavuza, lokufaka ekhatsi umhlabatsi wemabele, wema-ovari, wemaphaphu kanye newesifuba".
Indlela lefanako seyiphumelele ekwelapheni sifo semdlavuza wematsambo, ngekutsatsa emaseli emtimba wekulwa nekugula bese uwafundzisa kutsi angawatsintsa njani emaseli emdlavuza.
