I-HIV/AIDS: I-China ibika kukhula lokungu-14% kwetigameko letinsha
I-China imemetele kwenyuka lokungu-14 ekhulwini kwebantfu labane-HIV ne-AIDS.
Ngekusho kwetiphatsimandla tetemphilo, bantfu labangetulu kwa-820 000 kulelive banato.
Emkhatsini wa-2018, bantfu labangu-40 000 bagule ngalesifo.
Linyenti lalabantfu labasandza kutfola lesifo belisakatwa ngekwelicansi, lokukhombisa kutsi sekwenteke lokwehlukile.
Ngalokwetayelekile, i-HIV isakateke ngekushesha etindzaweni letitsite taseShayina ngekumpontshelwa ingati lenesifo.
Nanobe kunjalo, lokwenta kutsi bantfu bangangenwa yi-HIV kube shengatsi seyiphelile, kusho tikhulu tetemphilo taseShayina emhlanganweni lobewuse-Yunnan.
Umnyaka ngamunye, bantfu labane-HIV ne-AIDS eChina bandza ngalokungaba ngu-100 000.
Kutseleleka nge-HIV ngekwelicansi kuyinkinga lenkhulu emphakatsini we-LGBT waseChina.
Buntfu bebulili lobufanako buye bavalwa eChina nga-1997, kepha lubandlululo lwe-LGBT lusasakatekile.
Lucwaningo lukhombisa kutsi ngenca yemagugu lamasha alelive, emadvodza lalishumi kuya kumashumi lasikhombisa ekhulwini lalala nalamanye agcine ashade nalabasikati.
Etimeni letinyenti, tifo tihanjiswa ngenca yekungavikeleki kahle kwalaba labatsandzanako.
Kusukela nga-2003, hulumende waseShayina wetsembise kutsi utawuniketa wonkhe umuntfu imitsi yekulwa ne-HIV njengencenye yemitamo yekubukana naleligciwane.
