Kubikwa kutsi licembu lifuna kutsi baholi betinkampani banikete tisebenti tabo imali letawugcinwa ngulesiphitsiphitsi sekusebenta ngekusebentisa buhlakani lobungoti ngekutsi babanikete sikhatsi sekuphumula.
Loku bekutawenta kutsi tisebenti tijabulele emaviki lamatsatfu ekuphumula ngemholo lofanako.
Letindzaba titsi lombono "ufanelekile" eluhlelweni lwepolitiki lwelicembu futsi utawusita bantfu kutsi babe seluhlangotsini lwebasebenti.
I-Trade Union Congress yavuma kutsi kusetjentwe emalanga lamane ngeliviki kute tisebenti tizuze emnotfweni lotfutfukako.
Umuntfu lohloniphekile we-Labour Party watjela i-Sunday Times kutsi loluhlelo lolusha lutawumenyetelwa ekupheleni kwemnyaka.
Loku angeke kwenteke ngalanga linye, kepha liviki lekusebenta emalanga lamane  ngulona mgomo wetfu lohambisana nendlela yelicembu yekugucula umnotfo ube ngulozuzisa tisebenti kanye nelisu lelicembu letekukhicita jikelele.
I-Labor Party ayisiyo yekucala lefuna lomcondvo, ngobe i-Green Party yetsembisa emaviki lamane ekusebenteni ngesikhatsi semkhankhaso wayo welukhetfo wanga-2017.
Nanobe kunjalo, loku akukatsandvwa kakhulu licembu le-Labour.
Ummeli we-Labor Party watsi: "Liviki lekusebenta emalanga lamane akusilo licebo lelicembu futsi alibhekiswa kulo licembu".
Umkhansela longekho emtsetfweni, John McDonnell, wasebentisa umhlangano webaSebenti kuleliviki leliphelile kute acacise umbono wakhe wekugucula umnotfo ube wesitsotsi.
MacDonnell watsi utimisele kucedza emandla alabo "labangaboni buso" kanye nalaba "labatsengisako" betinkampani temanti.
Tinhlelo te-Shadow Chancellor tiphindze tisho kutsi banikati bemanti bangaphindze batfole sabelo sabo sonkhe ngobe hulumende we-Labor angenta 'kukhishwa' ngekubuka tintfo letingahambi kahle.
Waphindze wacinisekisa tinhlelo tekufaka tisebenti etikwebhodi tetinkampani kanye nekusungula imali yekubamba inkapani kute inike tisebenti 10% wetimali temabhizinisi angasese, letingazuza imali lengetulu kwa-£500 ngemnyaka.
Lindsey Graham naJohn Kennedy bakhuluma 60 Minutes ngekutsi ngabe luphenyo lwe-FBI ngaKavanagh lungagucula yini umbono wabo
Luphenyo lwe-FBI lwekuhlola emacala lacondziswe kuLusompempe Brett Kavanaugh lwabambezela kuvota kwekugcina ngekubekwa kwakhe njengeLusompempe lokungenani liviki linye futsi kuphakamisa umbuto wekutsi ngabe loku lokutfolwe yi-FBI kungenta yini kutsi kube khona ema-Senator ema-Republican lasekela Kavanaugh.
Kulengcoco leyaboniswa ngeLisontfo, Scott Pelley, umcoceli we-60 Minutes, wacoca nemaSenator aseRiphabhulikhi, John Kennedy naLindsey Graham, kutsi ngabe i-FBI ingahle itfole yini intfo letabenta bashintje umbono wabo.
Kennedy bekabonakala avulekile kwendlula umlingani wakhe waseNingizimu Carolina.
"Yebo", kwasho Kennedy.
