Kodvwa umbono waGram ngekubekwa kwelitsimba wahlala ucinile.
"Ngitimisele kakhulu ngaBret Kavanaugh, futsi umbono wami ungashintja kuphela ngekufakaza lokunemandla lalingana nelidayimani", washo njalo.
"Dokotela Ford, angati kutsi kwentekani, kepha yinye intfo lengiyati kutsi Brett ukuphikile konkhe loku", kwengeta Graham, akhuluma naChristine Blaise Ford.
