Yini i-Global Citizen Festival, futsi yente lutfo yini kunciphisa buphuya?
NgaLesihlanu, i-Global Citizen Festival , umkhosi wemculo wemnyaka lotawubanjwa yi-star band, itawugujwa e-New York City, futsi itawuba nemsebenti lobaluleke kakhulu wekucedza buphuya emhlabeni wonkhe.
Emnyakeni wayo wesikhombisa, i-World Citizens Festival, inetinkhulungwane tebantfu letibutsana endzaweni lenkhulu yase Central Park, hhayi nje kute tijabulele kudlala kwebaculi labafana naJanet Jackson, Cardi B na Shawn Mendes, kepha futsi kute tichaze inhloso yalomkhosi: kucedza buphuya lobukhulu nga-2030.
Umkhosi webahlali beMhlaba, lowacalwa nga-2012, uchubeka nemklamo wemhlaba wonkhe wekulwa nebuphuya lowentiwa licembu lemave emhlaba lelilwela emalungelo eluntfu, lelifuna kucedza buphuya ngekukhulisa linani lebantfu labakhutsatako.
Kute utfole lithikithi lemahhala kulomcimbi (ngaphandle nangabe ukulungele kukhokhela lithikithi le-VIP), bekufanele utibandzakanye emsebentini wekuvolontiya nobe utfumele i-imeyili kumholi wemhlaba, ushaye lucingo nobe wente lokunye nobe letinye tintfo letibalulekile letihlose kusita ekwandziseni kwati ngemgomo wakho wekucedza buphuya.
Kodvwa-ke, umkhosi webantfu bemhlaba uphumelele kangakanani kuleminyaka lengu-12 leyendlulile?
Ngabe lomcondvo wekutsi bantfu bavulelwe umkhosi ngekukhululeka ucinisile yini kutsi bantfu bafune kutsi bantfu bahambe, nobe ngulenye nje intfo lebitwa ngekutsi "kubutana" lapho bantfu bakholelwa khona kutsi benta umehluko mbamba ngekusayina sicelo nobe ngekutfumela umlayeto ku-Twitter?
Bahleli be-Global Citizen batsi kusukela nga-2011, lomkhosi ubhalise ngetento letingetulu kwetigidzi letingu-19 letentiwa ngulabo labawusekelako, labanetinhloso letehlukene.
Ngekwenta njalo, baholi bemhlaba batfume kutsi batakhipha imali lengetulu kwetigidzigidzi letingu-37 temadola aseMelika, letawutsintsa kuphila kwebantfu labangetulu kwetigidzigidzi letingu-2,25 nga-2030.
Ekucaleni kwa-2018, lelicembu lakhipha tifungo letingu-390 kanye netimemetelo letentiwe ngenca yetento talo, lokungenani tigidzigidzi letingu-10 temadola letakhokhwa nobe letatfolwa.
Lelicembu likhombisa kutsi lemali leniketwa bantfu, yenta kutsi kube nebantfu labacishe babe tigidzi letingu-649 emhlabeni wonkhe.
Lenye yetinhlelo letibalulekile letentelwe iNingizimu Afrika, yi-The Power of Nutrition: I-British Partnership yebasebentisi betimali kanye netati tekusebentisa, letibopheleke ekusiteni bantfwana kutsi bafinyelele emakhono abo, yetsembisa kuniketa iRwanda tigidzi temarandi letingu-35 kute isite ekucedzeni kungondleki kahle endzaweni yakitsi, ngemuva kwekutfola ema-tweet langetulu kwa-4 700 lavela kubantfu labatsintsekako ku-Global Citizens.
Ngekusekelwa nguhulumende wase UK, banikeli, bohulumende bemave kanye ne Global Citizens njengawe, singenta kungalungi ngekwesintfu lokumayelana nekungondleki kube yintfo leyenteka kadzeni,  kusho i-Ambassador ye Power of Nutrition Tracy Ullman ngesikhatsi semkhosi lochubekako eLondon nga-Ephreli 2018.
Lelicembu liphindze latsi ngemuva kwekutsatsa tinyatselo letingetulu kwa-5 000 tekucinisekisa kutsi i-UK iyasondla kahle bomake nebantfwana, hulumende umemetele kutsi utawuxhasa Umklamo we-Power of Nutrition, lotawuhlanganisa bantfu labasikati nebantfwana labatigidzi letisihlanu ngetinyatselo tekwenta ncono kudla.
