Kodvwa njengasemkhankasweni lomkhulu wekulwela emalungelo eluntfu kanye nalokulwa nelubandlululo, sitawuchubeka siphumelele ngobe sibambisene, sinemandla.
Janet Jackson, Weekend, Sean Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Moné  ngulabanye baculi labatawukhuluma kulomcimbi walo nyaka lotawubanjelwa e-New York, lotawubanjwa nguDeborah-Lee Ferness naHugh Jackman.
I-USA ingasebentisa umkhosi waselwandle kute uvimbele  kuhanjiswa kwemandla aseRussia: Indvuna yelitiko letasekhaya
INdvuna yeTasekhaya yaseMelika, Ryan Zinke, yatsi iWashington ingasebentisa umkhosi wayo wemikhumbi yemikhumbi uma kudzingeka, kuvikela kutsi tintfo taseRussia letitfwala emandla tingangeni etimakethe, kufaka ekhatsi eMphumalanga Lesekhatsi.
Zinke utsi kuba khona kweRussia eSyria, ikakhulukati lapho isebenta khona ngekumenywa nguhulumende losemtsetfweni, kuyindlela yekufuna timakethe letinsha temandla.
"Ngicabanga kutsi sizatfu sekutsi babe eMiddle East kutsi bafuna kutsengisa ngemandla ngendlela labenta ngayo eMpumalanga neYurophu, eningizimu yeYurophu", kusho yena.
Lomuntfu losesikhundleni utsi kunetindlela letitsite tekusombulula lenkinga.
"Emave aseMelika asebente nemikhumbi yetfu yemikhumbi kute kucinisekiswe kutsi imikhumbi yabo ivulekile futsi, uma kudzingeka, ivalwe kute emandla abo angangeni etimakethe", kusho Ndvuna.
Zinké wakhuluma nalabo lebebakhona kulomcimbi lobewuhlelwe yiConsumer Energy Alliance, licembu lelingasebenti ngekutsenga imali lelitibeka kutsi "livi lebasebentisi bemandla" eMelika.
Wachubeka wafananisa indlela iWashington leyenta ngayo emave aseRussia kanye ne-Iran, watsi tifanana.
Lisu le-Iran neRussia kutemnotfo  kungukusebentisa kahle kakhulu nekusebentisa lokunye kufutfumala, kusho lomphatsi, abita iRussia ngekutsi ngumkhontisindvo munye, umnotfo wayo lotsembele kumafutsa emvelo.
Letitatimende tentiwa ngenca yekutsi hulumende waTrump utibekele umgomo wekukhulisa kutsengiswa kwegesi yemvelo leyengetiwe eYurophu, esikhundleni seRussia leniketa indlela leshibhile kubatsengi baseYurophu.
Kute kwentiwe loku, tikhulu te Trump, kufaka ekhatsi Mengameli waseMelika Donald Trump, betama kwenta iGermany kutsi ishiye lomklamo we "North Stream-2" lowenta iBerlin ibe "siboshwa" se Moscow.
eMoscow, bekugcizelelwa kanyenti kutsi lomklamo we Nord Stream-2 lobita tigidzigidzi leti-11 temadola, lotawuphindza kabili emandla ekuhambisa lamapayipi kute kube tigidzigidzi leti-110 temamitha, ngumklamo wetemnotfo.
I-Kremlin itsi kuphikisa kwaWashington lokukhulu kuloluhlelo kubangelwa tintfo tetemnotfo futsi kuyindlela yekuncintisana lokungakalungi.
Ngigcizelela kutsi siyavumelana kutsi emandla agezi angeke abe yindlela yekucindzetela nekutsi batsengi kumele bakhone kukhetsa batsengisi,  kusho iNdvuna yeTemandla yaseRussia Alexander Novak ngemuva kwekuhlangana neNdvuna yeTemandla yaseMelika Rick Perry ngaSeptemba eMoscow.
Lesimo seMelika sabangela kuphikisana neJalimane, leyakhombisa kutibophelela kwayo kulomklamo.
Timboni taseJalimane letiboniswa yiBandla Letimboni taseJalimane (BDI), ticele iMelika kutsi ingahlanganyeli kutinhlelo te-EU tetemandla kanye netivumelwano temave lamabili emkhatsini we Berlin ne Moscow.
"Nangabe live lesitsatfu lingenelela ekunikeni kwetfu emandla agezi, loko kudala inkinga lenkhulu", kusho Dieter Kempf, inhloko yeBundesverband der Deutschen Industrie (BDI) ngemuva kwemhlangano weMengameli waseJalimane Angela Merkel neMengameli waseRussia Vladimir Putin.
Sishayamtsetfo saseMassachusetts Elizabeth Warren utawufundza ngekucophelela kutsi utawutiphakamisa yini kutsi abe ngumengameli nga-2020
Elizabeth Warren, lisenate laseMassachusetts, watsi ngeMgcibelo utawufundza ngekucophelela kutsi utawutibandzakanya yini kulenchubo yekumenyetelwa kuba ngumengameli ngemuva kwelukhetfo lwesikhashana.
Emhlanganweni weNdlu yeMasipala e-Holyoake, eMassachusetts, Warren wacinisekisa kutsi utawucabanga ngekungena kulomncintiswano.
"Sikhatsi sekutsi bafati baye eWashington bayolungisa hulumende wetfu lophukile, futsi loko kudzinga umfati losetulu", kusho Warren kuThe Hill.
Ngemuva kwaNovemba 6, ngitawucabangisisa ngekumenyetelwa kuba ngumengameli.
Warren wachaza umsebenti waMengameli Donald Trump ngesikhatsi semhlangano ngekutsi "uhambisa lesigodzi ngendlela lengasiyo".
"Ngikhatsateke kakhulu ngaloko lokwentiwa ngu Donald Trump ngentando yetfu yelinyenti", washo njalo.
Warren usola kakhulu Trump kanye nemuntfu labekangumengameli wemajaji aseNkantolo lePhakeme Brett Kavanaugh.
Kulolucwaningo, i-Warren yafaka ekhatsi kutsi "kufanele sibe neluphenyo lwe-FBI ngaphambi kwekutsi sicale kuvota".
Nanobe kunjalo, lucwaningo lolwentiwe ngaLesine lukhombise kutsi linyenti lebavoti labatsandza Warren, abacabangi kutsi kumele agijime nga-2020.
Ngekusho kweluphenyo lwe Suffolk University Political Research Center/Boston Globe, emaphesenti langemashumi lasihlanu nesiphohlongo ebavoti baseMassachusetts labangahle babe khona batsi lisekela lesigungu kumele lingakhetsi.
Ngalokwehlukile, bantfu labangu-32% bayasisekela lesimisomgomo.
Loluphenyo lukhombisa kutsi bantfu labanyenti bayamsekela Deval Patrick lobekangumbusi: 38 ekhulwini bayamsekela kutsi angahle abe khona elukhetfweni, kantsi 48% bayamphikisa.
Lamanye emabito labalulekile emaDemocrats laphikiswana ngawo mayelana nelisu la-2020 afaka ekhatsi Joe Biden lobekangumsekela waMengameli kanye na Bernie Sanders, losisebenti seSigungu Lesikhulu sase Vermont.
Biden utsi utawutsatsa sincumo ngalokusemtsetfweni ngaJanuary, kusho i-Associated Press.
Sarah Palin ukhulume ngekuphazamiseka kwengcondvo ngemuva kwekuhlupheka kwaTrump
Trek Palin, loneminyaka lengu-26, wajoyina libutfo lemasotja ngaSeptember, wacitsa umnyaka e-Iraq.
Waboshwa futsi wabekwa licala lekuhlukunyetwa ekhaya ngeMsombuluko ebusuku.
"Indvodzana yami lebuyele ekhaya, seyiva buhlungu lobufana nebazalwane labane-PTSD futsi labalimatile, kantsi emasotja etfu abuya alunywe", washo nakakhuluma naDonald Trump eTulsa, e-Oklahoma.
Palin wababita ngekutsi "ngumkhovu emehlweni" futsi watsi ngendvodzana yakhe kanye nalamanye emaveteran emphini: "Bayabuya sebagucuke, batibuta kutsi ngabe bayabatsatsa yini labo labadlala nabo, emasotja, ema-pilots kanye nalamanye emasotja ngendlela labahlonipha ngayo live labo".
Thack Palin waboshwa ngeMsombuluko eWasillah, e-Alaska, futsi wabekwa licala lekuhlukunyetwa ngekhatsi ekhaya, lokungenelela kulokungcola kanye nekuphatsa tikhali ngesikhatsi adzakiwe, ngekusho kwaDan Bennett, ummeli weLitiko Lemaphoyisa eWasillah.
Tifundza letingu-18 kanye ne-D.C. tiyamukela lenchabhayi yetinchubo letinsha tekukhosela.
Emave langu-18 kanye ne-D.C. asekela kuphikisana ngekwemtsetfo nenchubomgomo lensha yaseMelika levimbela kutsi bantfu lababalekile nobe labahlukunyetiwe basekhaya batfole siphephelo.
Ngekusho kwe-NBC News, bameleli betifundza kanye netigodzi letingu-18 bafaka incwadzi levela enkantolo ngaLesihlanu eWashington, DC, lemayelana nekusekela umceli webukhosela lobeka lomtsetfo.
Ligama leliphelele lemmangali ku-Grace v. Sessions, lowafakwa yi-American Civil Liberties Union nga-Agasti macondzana netinchubo tahulumende wasekhaya, alishicilelwa.
Lomake utsi indvodza yakhe lengasiyo isakhamuti saseMelika kanye nemadvodzana akhe labesebandleni lebugebengu bamphatsa kabi, kodvwa ngaJulayi 20 tiphatsimandla taseMelika tamlahla loMake ngekumniketa siphephelo.
Wabanjwa eTexas.
Bameli betifundza labasekela Grace batsi i-El Salvador, iHonduras neGuatemala bafaka ticelo letinyenti tekukhoseliswa eMelika, njengobe emave abhekene netinkinga letinyenti tebugebengu kanye nebudlova basemakhaya.
Umtsetfo lomusha waseMelika wekukhishwa kwebabaleki ususe sincumo lesentiwa nguMkhandlu Wetifundza Wekufaka Sicelo Ngababaleki nga-2014 lesasivumela bantfu labangenabo emalungelo labatsintsekako lababalekela budlova basemakhaya kutsi bafake sicelo sekukhishwa kwebabaleki.
Umshushisi Jikelele we-District of Columbia, Carl Racine, washo ngesitatimende sakhe ngaLesihlanu kutsi lenchubomgomo lensha "ayinakekeli emashumi eminyaka yekusebentisa umtsetfo wasekhaya, wesifundza kanye newemave emhlaba".
Umtsetfo wesifundza udzinga kutsi tonkhe ticelo tekukhishwa kwesimemo sekukhoseliswa tihlolwe ngekwesisekelo semicimbi letsite kanye netimo, futsi loku kwephula lomgomo, kusho umeluleki wetemtsetfo.
Bameli baphindze batsi imitsetfo yekungavumeli bantfu kutsi bangene kulelive ilimaza umnotfo waseMelika, bagcizelela kutsi bantfu labatsite labatsandza kuba bosomabhizinisi "bacinisekisa kutsi banetisebenti letidzingekako".
NgaJune, Umshushisi Jikelele Jeff Sessions wayala behluleli betekufika kutsi bangabe basakhokha bantfu lababalekela budlova basemakhaya nobe belicembu letigelekece.
"Bantfu labafuna kuba ngulabahlala eveni labo ngenca yekuhlukunyetwa nobe kwesaba ngenca yebuhlanga, inkholo, buve, nobe buve babo nobe tinkholelo tepolitiki batawuniketwa siphephelo", kwasho Sessions ngesitatimende sakhe samhlaka-11 Inhlaba.
Lelithuluzi belingakaze lihlelwe kutsi licatulule tonkhe tinkinga, ngisho naletinkhulu kakhulu bantfu lababhekana nato onkhe malanga emhlabeni wonkhe.
Umsebenti Wekusindzisa Bantfu ePalu: Linani Lebantfu Labafile Liyaphindvwa Kabili
Bantfu labasindza kulenkinga bebahlupheka kakhulu.
