Ummeli waseMelika usola iChina ngekuhlaselwa ngekusebentisa "tindzaba tekukhangisa"
Ngemuva kweliviki linye lelinye liphephandaba lelisemtsetfweni lase China liphephe sikhangiso semakhasi lamane ephephandzabeni laseMelika lelikhuluma ngekuhwebelana lokuzuzisako kwe US ne China, ummeli wase US e China usole iBeijing ngekusebentisa emaphephandzaba ase US ekusakazeni inkhulumo-mphikiswano.
Mengameli waseMelika Donald Trump, ngaLwesitsatfu, wabhekisa kuDes Moines Register China Daily, liphephandaba lelikhulu lase-Iowa, ngekusola iChina ngekungenela lukhetfo lwe-US Congress lolutawuba ngaNovemba 6.
Kusola kwaTrump kutsi iBeijing yetama kungenela lukhetfo lwaseMelika, kucinisekisa loko lokwatiswa tiphatsimandla taseMelika ku-Reuters: kutsi sekusikhatsi lesisha sekucinisa umkhankhaso waseWashington wekucindzetela iChina.
Nanobe kungumkhuba wabohulumende bangaphandle kutsi babeke tikhangiso kute batfutfukise kutsengiselana, iBeijing neWashington nyalo sebatselela emphini yekutsengiselana, lokwenta kutsi babhadale tintfo letingeniswa ngemave abo.
I-China yabhadala ngekuhambisa imali etintfweni letitsite ngesikhatsi kucala imphi yekuhwebelana, loku bekuhloselwe kutsi kushaywe bantfu labatsengisa tintfo letitsite etindzaweni letinjenge-Iowa, lebebasekela licembu le-Republican laTrump, kusho tati tase-China netaseMelika.
Terry Branstad, ummeli waseMelika eChina kanye nembusi wangaphambilini wesikhatsi lesidze wase-Iowa, lekungumkhicito lomkhulu wetekulima lohanjiswa eChina, utsi iBeijing ilimaze tisebenti taseMelika, balimi kanye nemabhizinisi.
I-China, Branstad ubhala endzabeni levela ku-Des Moines Register yangeLisontfo, "nyalo seyiphindzaphindza lokuhlukumeta ngekutsi ibeke titfombe tekukhangisa emshinini wetfu lotimele".
"Ngekuhambisa inkhulumo yakhe, hulumende waseChina usebentisa emasiko aseMelika lasitsandza kakhulu enkhululeko yekukhuluma kanye neyekuhambisa emaphepheni ngekukhokhela nekukhangisa kuDes Moines Register", kusho Branstad.
Kepha etitolo temaphephandzaba lapha etitaladini tasePeking, awufuni kuva emavi laphikisako nobe ubone umehluko mbamba wemibono bantfu baseChina labangase bahlangane nawo uma bati ngemasu etemnotfo aseChina, ngobe imidiya yasekhaya ilawulwa kakhulu yiCominist Party yaseChina, uyabhala.
