Bacwaningi bayacwayisa: ngekuhambisa iCavana, emaRephabliki ayabacindzetela bantfu labasikati labafuna kukhetsa ngesikhatsi lesisemkhatsini
Bantfu labanyenti labaphakeme be-Republican bakhetsa kuhlala eceleni futsi basekela kukhetfwa kwa-Justice Brett Kavanaugh, nanobe kunetinsolo tekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicansi, futsi bacwaningi bayacwayisa kutsi loku kungahle kubonakale kungasebenti kahle, ikakhulukati kubantfu labasikati, lokungahle kubangele kukhetfwa kwa-Justice Kavanaugh.
Umphumela waloko waba kutsi bantfu labanyenti baseRiphabhulikhi batise kutsi bafuna kuchubeka nekuvota.
Grant Rier, longuphrofesa wetembusave esikolweni saMackSwell University eSiracus, wabhala sihloko lesashicilelwa ngaMgcibelo.
Rier uyabuta kutsi ngabe imitamo yaMengameli Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) yekwenta luphenyo lwe-FBI, lolwentiwe emaminithini ekugcina, itawuba yanele yini kutsi ivale imilomo yebavoti labatsukutsele.
"Bantfu labasikati angeke bakukhohlwe lokwenteka itolo, angeke bakukhohlwe kusasa nobe ngaNovemba", kwasho Carine Jean-Pierre, umeluleki lomkhulu kanye nemkhulumeli wavelonkhe welicembu lelihamba embili i-MoveOn, ephepheni laseWashington, D.C.
NgaLesihlanu ekuseni, babhikishi bahlabela batsi "November ahead!" embikweSenate ngesikhatsi emaRepublican lalawula iKomidi yeTemtsetfo akhetsa kukhetsa Kavanaugh, nanobe bekunembiko waDokotela Christine Blasey Ford, kubika iMic.
"Kucinisa intsandvo yelinyenti kanye nekukhutsata kutawuphuma kuleso simo", kusho umcwaningi wetembusave longenawo emacembu, Stu Rothenberg, ku-website yetindzaba.
Bantfu batsi simo sesiphelile, futsi kuliciniso loko.
Kodvwa tintfo tingaba timbi kakhulu, ikakhulukati kubavoti labasikati labasemaphandleni kanye nalabaseminyakeni lengu-18 kuya ku-29 budzala, labangafuni kuba nemengameli kodvwa bavame kungatifaki emacenjini abo ekuvota.
Ngisho nangaphambi kwekutsi Ford afakaze embikwebantfu ngekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicansi, bacwaningi bebacabanga kutsi uma ngabe emaRephabliki avuma kutsi nguye lotawukhetfwa, loku kungabangela kuphendvuka.
"Loku sekuliphutsa lelikhulu elicembu lemaRepublican", kusho Michael Steele, lobekangusihlalo welikomidi le-Republican National Committee, ekucaleni kweliviki leliphelile, njengoba kubikwa yi-NBC News.
"Loku akusiyo nje kuphela mayelana nekuvota kwelikomidi nobe kuvotelwa kwekugcina nobe kutsi ngabe Kavanaugh uhleti yini enkantolo, kepha nekutsi emaRephabliki ayisebentisa njani, kutsi amtsatsa njani", kusho Guy Cecil, longumcondzisi we Priorities USA, licembu lelisita kukhetsa emaDemocrats, kulesiteshi setindzaba.
Nanobe kunjalo, bantfu baseMelika babonakala behlukene ekhatsi mayelana nekutsi ngubani lokufanele bametsembe - ngu-Ford nobe ngu-Kavanaugh, futsi batsandza kakhulu lona wekugcina.
Luhlolo lolusha lwe-YouGov lukhombisa kutsi 41% webantfu labaphendulile bayakholwa nobe bavumelana naloko lokushiwo ngu-Ford, kantsi 35% batsi bayakholwa nobe bavumelana na-Cavanaugh.
Ngetulu kwaloko, bantfu labangu-38% bakholelwa kutsi Cavanaugh abekadze acamba emanga ngesikhatsi afakaza, kantsi bantfu labangu-30% kuphela labasho lokufanako ngaFord.
Ngekucelwa nguFlake, i-FBI nyalo iyaphenya ngetinsolo letetfulwe nguFord, kanye nalomunye umbekwacala longu-Deborah Ramirez, kusho i-The Guardian.
Emasontfweni lambalwa lengcile, Ford wafakaza ecaleni lakhe eKomidini yeTemtsetfo yaseSenate kutsi Cavanaugh, ngesikhatsi adzakiwe, wamhlasela nakaneminyaka lengu-17.
