Umsunguli we-World Wide Web uhlela kusungula i-Internet lensha ye-Google ne-Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, umsunguli we-World Wide Web, ucala inhlangano lekhutsatako kute acudzelane ne-Facebook, i-Amazon ne-Google.
Umklamo wekugcina we-tech legend, i-Inrupt, yinkampani lesekelwe ku-platform levulekile ye-Berners-Lee Solid.
I-Solid ivumela basebentisi kutsi bakhetse kutsi batawugcina kuphi idatha yabo nekutsi bobani labatawutfola lwati.
Kulenkhulumo lecondzile ye-Fast Company, Berners-Lee wahleka watsi Inrupt ifuna kubusa umhlaba wonkhe.
"Kufanele sikwente nyalo", usho njalo nakakhuluma ngalentfo yakhe yekucala.
"Lona ngumzuzu lomcoka".
Lolusito lusebentisa iSolid Technology, lekwenta bantfu bakhone kwakha ema-database abo labatifunela wona nobe ema-POD.
Ungafaka ekhatsi luhla lwebantfu lochumana nabo, tintfo lotentako, ikhalenda, umtapo wetingoma kanye naletinye tintfo tekusebenta.
Loluhlelo lusebenta ngendlela lefanako ne-Google Drive, iMicrosoft Outlook, Slack ne-Spotify  konkhe kungasetjentiswa kusiphequluli sinye ngesikhatsi sinye.
Lokwenta indzawo yekugcina imininingwane ye-Internet ibe ngeyehlukile kutsi ilawulwa ngumsebentisi, longatfola nobe nguyiphi imininingwane layidzingako.
