Ngekusho kwa John Bruce, CEO walelikhamphani, umcondvo we Inrupt kutsi inkampani inikete imitfombolusito, tinchubo kanye nemakhono lafanele kwenta kutsi iSolid itfolakale kubo bonkhe bantfu.
Nyalo, lenkapani inebantfu labafaka ekhatsi Berners-Lee, Bruce, luhlaka lwekuphepha lolutsengwe yi-IBM, bantfu labambalwa labatsite labatsite labatsenge umsebenti wekusebenta kulomklamo, kanye nemphakatsi webantfu labatinikele.
Kusukela kuleliviki, batfutfukisi betemnotfo emhlabeni wonkhe batawukwati kwakha tinhlelo tabo tekusebentisa tintfo letingasetjentiswa ngumuntfu ngamunye basebentisa emathulusi latfolakala kuwebhusayithi ye-Inrupt.
Berners-Lee watsi yena nelicembu lakhe abatsintsani ne-Facebook ne-Google mayelana nekutsi ngabe inkampani yakhe kufanele yini yente tingucuko letinkhulu letitawenta kutsi yonkhe imishini yabo igucuke ngalokuphelele ngalobunye busuku.
"Asikuceli imvume kubo".
Kulombhalo wakhe ku Medium lowabhalwa ngeMgcibelo, Berners-Lee wabhala kutsi "umsebenti we Inrupt" kuniketa emandla etentengiselwano kanye nemvelo yekulondvolota bucotfo nekhwalithi yenethiwekhi lensha leyakhiwe ku Solid.
Nga-1994, Berners-Lee wagucula i-Internet ngekusungula i-World Wide Web Consortium eMassachusetts Institute of Technology.
Etinyangeni letimbalwa letengcile, livi laBerners-Lee belikhona kakhulu etingcocweni tekungatingeneli tindzaba te-Internet.
Ngisho nobe angacala i-Inrupt, Berners-Lee utawuhlala angumsunguli kanye nemcondzisi we-World Wide Web Consortium, i-Internet Foundation kanye ne-Open Data Institute.
"Nginelitsemba lelikhulu ngalelitfuba lelilandzelako le-Internet", kusho Berners-Lee.
