Umfundisi Bernard Vann watfola lomklomelo mhlaka 29 Inyoni 1918 ngekuhlanganyela ekuhlaseleni iBellenglish neLewcourt.
Kodvwa-ke, kwatsi ngemuva kwemalanga lamane wabulawa ngumbulali lomkhulu, wangete watfola kutsi utfole umklomelo lomkhulu waseBrithani.
