Ngekusho kwephephandaba lase London langa 29 Inyoni 1918, indvuna yelicembu le-Vann yahola licembu layo le-battalion lelidlula eSen-Kanten Canal, ngesikhatsi kunenkungu lenkhulu futsi lidubule kakhulu.
Ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi, watiphonsa emgceni wekulwa futsi ngekutimisela wahola licembu lakhe, wase ulahla sibhamu sakhe ngesandla sinye, wabulala emasotja lamatsatfu.
Luphondvo-jikelele Vann wabulawa ngumuntfu lobekahlasela emaJalimane nga-October 4, 1918  lokwakusele inyanga yinye kuphela kutsi imphi iphele.
Umtukulu walesitfunti, Michael Vann, loneminyaka lengu-72, watsi bekangeke akhone kwenta intfo lefanana naleyo, kodvwa loko bekumkhutsata.
Yena nemnakabo Dokotela James Vann nabo babeka umchele ekupheleni kwemkhosi lowawuholwa yi-Imperial Youth Orchestra yase Brentwood.
