"Kusasa sinemidlalo le-12 lebalulekile, kodvwa nifuna kutsi iphele masinyane, njengobe kwenteka eBrooklyn, njengobe kwenteka eMedina.
Nangabe sicalo sihamba ngendlela yinye, kuba nemfutfo lomkhulu kubadlali labasemkhatsini.
Ngako-ke, saphindze sakha luhlelo lwetfu lwemdlalo futsi sabalungiselela ngendlela lebesicabanga kutsi ilungile, futsi kusasa sitawetama kwenta umangaliso.
Thomas wanikwa umsebenti wekuzama kuhola umzabalazo, wahlangana na Rory McIlroy emdlalweni lomkhulu na Paul Casey, Justin Rose, John Ram, Tommy Fleetwood na Ian Polter, kanye nalabanye badlali base Europe labasetulu.
"Ngikhetse lelicembu lemadvodza, futsi ngilandzelana, ngobe ngibona kutsi ngaleyo ndlela batawuvala tonkhe tintfo letingaba khona", kusho Bjorn, akhuluma ngekukhetsa kwakhe badlali labatsite.
Kusetjentiswa kwemkhumbi lomusha wemphi waseJalimane kuphindze kwabekwa eceleni
Lelinye libutfo lemphi lelisandza kuphuma emkhosini waseJalimane bekufanele lisebente nga-2014 kute litfole letinye tikebhe letindzala letatisebenta ngesikhatsi semphi lebandzako, kepha angeke kwenteke lokungenani emnyakeni lotako ngenca yetinhlelo letingasebenti kahle kanye nekukhula kwetindleko, kusho imisakato yalapha ekhaya.
Kufakwa kwelisiko le "Rheinland-Pfalz", umkhumbi lomusha kakhulu we Baden-Württemberg class, nyalo sekuhleliwe kuya engcenyeni yekucala ya-2019, kubika i-Die Zeit icondzisa kummeleli wemphi.
Lomkhumbi bekufanele ujoyine umbutfo wemkhumbi nga 2014, kepha tinkinga letenteka ngemuva kwekutfunyelwa, taletsa tinkinga kuloluhlelo.
Letinkhumbi letine telicembu lase Baden-Württemberg, letatsengwa ngemkhumbi wemkhumbi ngemnyaka wa 2007, titotsatsa sikhundla semikhumbi leguga kakhulu yelicembu lase Bremen.
Ngekusho kwemlandvo, batawuba nemasotja lamakhulu, ema-anti-aircraft kanye nemakhemikhali ekuhlasela, kanye netintfo letitsite letitsite letitsite, njengekucinisa i-radar, i-infrared kanye ne-acoustic signatures.
Letinye tintfo letibalulekile tifaka ekhatsi sikhatsi lesidze sekusebenta  kumele kube nekusebenta kwemaphenyane lasandza kutfolwa sikhatsi lesingaba yiminyaka lemibili khashane nemahhovisi emakhaya.
Nanobe kunjalo, kubambezeleka kwekusebentisa lemikhumbi kusho kutsi lemikhumbi lemikhulu yemphi lekutsiwa itawenta iJalimane ikhone kusakata emandla ayo emaveni angaphandle, itawube seyisebenta, kusho i-Die Zeit.
Loluchungechunge lwekulwa netimphi lolubitwa ngekutsi yi-F125 lwaba setindzabeni temlandvo ngemnyaka lophelile ngesikhatsi libutfo lemphi laseJalimane liyekela kusebentisa lomkhumbi futsi liwubuyisela eBlohm & Voss eHamburg.
Loku kwaba kwekucala kutsi iNavy ibuyisele umkhumbi wayo emuva ekwakheni umkhumbi ngemuva kwekutfunyelwa.
Kuncane lokwatiswa ngetizatfu tekubuya, kepha bomasiko baseJalimane bacaphuna tinombolo letibucayi "tinkinga teluhlelo kanye netintfo letisetjentiswako" letenta kutsi umkhumbi wemphi ungasetjentiswa emphini.
Tinkinga teluhlelo belubaluleke kakhulu, njengoba imikhumbi yelibanga lase Baden-Württemberg itawusetjentiswa ngemalunga emkhumbi lacishe abe ngu 120  kuphela incenye yemsebenti wemkhumbi lomdzala welibanga lase Bremen.
Ngetulu kwaloko, kwabonakala kutsi lomkhumbi unesisindvo lesimatima, lokwenta kutsi ungabi nemandla futsi kunciphise emandla embutfo wemikhumbi kutsi wente lushintjo esikhatsini lesitako.
Kutsiwa le Rhineland-Pfalz lenemathani latinkhulungwane letisikhombisa inesisindvo lesisetulu kabili kunemikhumbi lefanako lebeyisetjentiswa ngemaJalimane emphini yemhlaba yesibili.
Ngetulu kwemishini lephukile, tindleko talomklamo, lokufaka ekhatsi kuceceshwa kwelicembu, nato tiyingoti.
Kutsiwa seyifinyelele kuma-euro latigidzigidzi letingu-3.1 (emadola latigidzi letingu-3.6) uma kucatsaniswa nema-euro latigidzigidzi letingu-2.2.
Tinkinga tekugcina emakhumbi lamasha aseme emahange tibaluleke kakhulu ngenca yeticwayiso takamuva tekunciphisa emandla aseJalimane.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka Hans-Peter Bartels, loyinhloko yelikomidi lekuvikela lephalamende yaseJalimane, wavuma kutsi libutfo lemphi lemkhumbi "lisuke seliphelelwa ngemikhumbi yekusebentisa".
Lesikhulu satsi lenkinga yakhula njengobe tikebhe letindzala betikhishwa emsebentini kodvwa tingakaze tibuyiselwe.
Watsi kute ngisho munye umkhumbi we Baden-Württemberg lowake watsatfwa ngemkhumbi.
I-National Trust Iphindze Ivule Tindlubu Letimfihlo
Lucwaningo lolusha lolwentiwe endzaweni yaseScotland, lufuna kubona kutsi bomanyovu bayisebentisa njani indzawo kute batfole kudla.
Kutawutsiwa lolwati lolutfolakale lutawusita ekuhloleni indlela letivame kutiphatsa ngayo tilwane letinetimphiko letincane futsi lusite ekuvikeleni loluhlobo.
Lucwaningo loluhlelwe bososayensi baseScotland National Trust, lutawuhlola emantongomane lasemancane, emantongomane lasetulu, kanye nemantongomane lamudze lanetinwele letinsundvu kanye nemantongomane lase Dobanton, lahlala e-Inverewe Gardens, eWester Ross.
Tintfo tekubhala letitsite titawufakwa etindzaweni letitsite letitungelete lendzawo kute tihlole indlela emalulwane lasebenta ngayo ngesikhatsi semnyaka.
Tisebenti te-NHS kanye netisebenti letititsandzako nato titawenta luhlolo lolusendzaweni letfwelwe ngesandla.
Kuhlolwa lokwentiwe ngekucophelela kwato tonkhe letintfo kutakwenta kutsi kubonakale kutsi tikhala kangakanani futsi tiphi tintfo letentiwa ngulamanye emacembu aletilwane.
Ngemuva kwaloko, kutawubese kwakhiwa imephu yetindzawo tekuhlala bese kubikwa kutsi kutawuba nemfanekiso locacile wekutiphatsa kwato endzaweni yonkhe.
Rob Dewar, longumeluleki we-NTS weTendzawo Letigcinwe, unembono wekutsi lemiphumela itawukhombisa kutsi nguyiphi indzawo lemcoka kakhulu kubologwaja nekutsi leminye imindeni iyisebentisa njani.
Lolwati lutakusita kutsi ubone tindlela letinkhulu tekuphatsa indzawo yekuhlala, njengekwakheka kwetihlahla, kanye netindlela tekugcina tihlahla tihlelelekile kutsi tingasebenta kahle kubologwaja kanye naletinye tilwane letihlobene nabo.
Emashumi eminyaka leyengcile, linani lemabhungane eScotland naseNgilandi lonkhe lehle kakhulu.
Tisetingotini tekunyamalala ngenca yekwakhiwa kwetindlu kanye nekutfutfukiswa kwetakhiwo, lokutsintsana nendzawo yato kanye nekulahlekelwa yindzawo yato.
Imishini yekucedza umoya nekukhanyisa kungaba yingoti, kufana nelucwebu lwekugcina timphungane, kusebentisa emakhemikhali ekwakha kanye nekuzingela emakati.
Ecinisweni, labologwaja abasibo timphumphutse.
Nobe kunjalo, indlela yato yekuzingela ebusuku yenta kutsi tindlebe tato tisebente kakhulu kunemehlo ato ekudleni.
Basebentisa indlela lenetintfo letinkhulu tekubonisa kutsi kukhona yini lokungabavimbela kutsi bangayi.
I-NTS, leyenta imisebenti yekunakekela takhiwo temlandvo letingetulu kwa-270, tibhidvo letingu-38 letibalulekile kanye nemhlaba longemahekitha langu-76 000 eveni lonkhe, itsatsa kakhulu tintfo letimayelana nemabhungane.
Lencenye inebantfu labangu-10 labaceceshiwe labatiwako labatihlola njalo, bahambe bayewuhlola futsi ngaletinye tikhatsi benta umsebenti wekusindzisa.
LeNhlangano yenta indzawo yekucala futsi leyodvwa yaseScotland yekugcina emantongomane endzaweni yaseThreave eDumphries naseGalloway, lapho kuhlala khona tilwane letisiphohlongo kuletilishumi.
Umphatsi wetakhiwo, David Thompson, utsi lendzawo iyindzawo lekahle kubo.
Utsi: "Lapha eThreave, yindzawo lenhle yekuhlala emalulwane".
Kunetakhiwo letindzala, tihlahla letindzala, netintfo letitsite tekuhlala kahle.
Kodvwa kunyenti lokungazange kwatiwe ngemalulwane, ngako umsebenti lesitawukwenta lapha nakuletinye tindzawo utasisita kutsi sivisise kabanti kutsi yini ledzingekako kute aphile kahle.
Uphindze akhumbule kutsi kubalulekile kuhlola kutsi kunemagundvwane yini ngaphambi kwekulungisa indzawo letsite, ngobe kubulala sikhonyane sinye kungabulala tilwane letinsikati letingu-400 kanye nemantjwele ato, futsi kungenteka kubulale ngisho netilwane tasendzaweni.
Emabhungane avikelwe ngumtsetfo, kubulala, kuhlukubeta noma kubulala indzawo yawo yekuhlala kungekho emtsetfweni.
Elizabeth Ferrell, longumcondzisi we-Scottish Bat Foundation, ucela lusito emphakatsini.
Utsi: "Kunyenti lesisengakakufundza ngemalulwane, kodvwa asati kutsi tiphila njani letinye tilwane letinyenti".
Ronaldo uphika kutsi wadlwengula futsi bommeli bakhe batomangalela magazini waseJalimane
Cristiano Ronaldo uphika emacala ekudlwengula labekwe wona, ngekutsi "tindzaba letingemanga" nekutsi bantfu bafuna nje kutitfoba ngekusebentisa ligama lakhe.
Bameli bakhe batfumela licala kumagazini wetindzaba waseJalimane i-Spiegel, lowakhipha emacala lamelene nalomdlali.
