Kubikwa kutsi wamkhokhela $375,000 kutsi akhulume ngalendzaba, kubika i-Spiegel ngeLesihlanu.
Ekukhulumeni kule-Instagram video, lenalelibhola letinyawo lelinebalandeli labatigidzi leti-142, emahora lambalwa ngemuva kwekubikwa kwetinsolo, Ronaldo, loneminyaka lengu-33 budzala, wachaza lolwati ngekutsi "tindzaba letingemanga".
"Cha, cha, cha, cha, cha.
Loku labakucoce lamuhla - konkhe kungumbiko longemanga - kusho umncobi weBallon d'Or emahlandla lasihlanu ngekhatsi ekhamera.
Batama kutiphakamisa ngekusebentisa ligama lami.
Loko kuyintfo levamile.
Bafuna kwatiwa ngekusho libito lami, kodvwa loko kuyincenye yemsebenti wabo.
"Ngiyindvodza lejabulako futsi konkhe kuhamba kahle", kwasho lomdlali amoyitela.
Bameli baRonaldo balungiselela kumangalela i-Spiegel ngetinsolo labatsi "tintfo letingavunyelwa mayelana nekungatsembeki kwemfihlo", ngekusho kwe-Reuters.
Ummeli wakhe, Christian Schertz, watsi lomdlali ufuna kuhlawuliswa "ngenca yekulimala ngekwesimilo, lokulingana nebubi lobentiwe, lokungenteka kutsi ngulokunye kwekwephulwa kwemalungelo ebantfu eminyakeni lembalwa leyengcile".
Kutsiwa lesento senzeka ngaJuni 2009 ehhotela lase Palms Hotel and Casino eLas Vegas.
Ngemuva kwekuhlangana kulelo khlabhu, Ronaldo naMayorga batsi babuyela ekamelweni laLonhlanhla, lapho abemdlwengule khona, ngekusho kwemiculu leyetfulwe eNkantolo yase-Clark, eNevada.
Mayorga utsi ngemuva kwaloludzaba, Ronaldo wawela ngemadvolo embikwabo wase utsi ungu 99% umfana lokahle, kepha munye% longakalungi.
