Mayorga uphindze atsi wacela emaphoyisa kutsi amtsatse titfombe temivimba yakhe, kodvwa kamuva wavuma kutsi kube nekuhlanganiswa kwetinkinga ngaphandle kwenkantolo ngobe bekesaba kutsi "utawutfola imphindziselo" futsi "etfuke kutfotjiswa embikwebantfu".
Lomfati loneminyaka lengu-34 budzala utsi nyalo wetama kushintja indzawo yakhe yekuhlala ngobe uchubeka nekuva buhlungu lobukhulu ngenca yaloko lokwenteka.
Ronaldo bekafuna kujoyina iReal Madrid esuka eManchester United ngesikhatsi sekuhlaselwa, kepha kulenyanga yehlobo watfutsela eItaly eJuve ngemali lengemarandi latigidzi letilikhulu.
Brexit: UK Lamula ngemakethe yemoto lelahlekile phakadze
Greg Clark, Indvuna Yetemabhizinisi, watsi i-UK "itawuzisola ngalokuphelele" uma i-Brexit ingenta kutsi ilahlekelwe sitfunti sayo sekuba ngumholi wemhlaba wekukhicita timoto.
Waphindze waphawula ngelwati lolutsi Toyota UK yatjela iBBC kutsi uma iUK iphuma e-EU ngaphandle kwekutfola sivumelwano, itawumisa kwesikhashana umkhicito endzaweni yayo eBernaston, edvute naseDerby.
"Sifuna kutsengiselana", kusho Mnu. Clark.
Umkhicito wetimoto waseJapan utsi kubambezeleka emnceleni uma ngabe kungekho sivumelwano se-Brexit kungaholela ekulahlekelweni kwemisebenti.
Lesakhiwo saseBernaston sakha ema-Toyota Auris kanye nema-Avensis, futsi ngemnyaka lophelile sakhicita cishe timoto letingu-150,000, lokungaba ngu-90% wato letatfunyelwa kulamanye emave aseYurophu.
"Ngicabanga kutsi uma i-UK ishiya i-EU ekupheleni kwaMarch, umkhicito usuke sewuvele uyekile", kusho Marvin Cook, umphatsi we-Toyota eBernaston.
Labanye bakhiciti betimoto baseBrithani bakhulume ngekukhatsateka ngekuphuma e-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano sekuhwebelana nemave emhlaba, lokufaka ekhatsi iHonda, iBMW neJaguar Land Rover.
Sibonelo, iBMW itsi itawuvala siteshi sayo seMini e-Oxford ngemuva kwenyanga i-Brexit iphelile.
Lokubangela kukhatsateka kutsi bakhiciti betimoto batsi uma kungabi khona sivumelwano se-Brexit, tinchubo tekuphakela titobese tibekwa engotini lenkhulu.
Umklamo we-Toyota ucala kusebenta ngesikhatsi, kantsi tincenye temoto letakhiwe ngesicelo tihanjiswa ngulabo labatsengisa e-UK nase-EU njalo ngemizuzu lengu-37.
Nangabe i-UK iphuma e-EU ingakenti sivumelwano ngaMarch 29, kutawuba netinkinga emnceleni, lokusho kutsi kungenta kubambezeleka kanye nekushoda kwetingcezu.
Ngekusho kwalelikhamphani, iToyota angeke ikhone kugcina tintfo letitsite embonini yayo leseDerbyshire sikhatsi lesidze kunelilanga linye, ngako-ke umkhicito utawumiswa.
UMnumzane Clark watsi luhlelo lwa Theresa May lolwakhishwa eCheckers mayelana nebuhlobo bakhe ne-EU "luhlelwe kahle kute kugwenywe kuhlolwa kwemincele".
"Sidzinga sivumelwano. Sifuna kwenta sivumelwano lesincono lesingasenta, ngiphindze ngitsi, singagcini ngekuphumelela nyalo, kodvwa sisebentise lelitfuba esikhatsini lesitako", washo kulenhlelo ye-BBC Radio 4 "Lamuhla".
"Hhayi nje iToyota kuphela, kepha nalabanye bakhiciti batsi kumele sikhone kulondvolota tinchubo tekuphakela letinemphumelelo".
I-Toyota ayizange ikwati kuchaza kutsi kutawumiswa sikhatsi lesingakanani, kepha esikhatsini lesidze, yacaphela kutsi tindleko letengetiwe titawenta kutsi lesihlahla singabi nemandla futsi ekugcineni siholele ekunciphiseni imisebenti.
Peter Tswalaris, losebente eBernaston iminyaka lengu-24 futsi loyinhloko ye-Union, utsi kukhatsateka kwemalunga alelihhovisi kukhula: "Kwetifundvo tami, uma silahlekelwa ngulemisebenti angeke sikhone kuyibuyisela".
Sikhulumi sahulumende sitsi: Sente luhlelo lolucondzile nalolucinile lwebudlelwane betfu ne-EU.
Umhlangano waTrump naRosenstein ungahle uhlehliswe futsi, ngekusho kweNdlu Lemhlophe.
Umhlangano waDonald Trump neLisekela Lemshushisi Jikelele Rod Rosenstein "ungahlehliselwa kulenye liviki" njengobe kulwa kwe Brett Kavanaugh kutsi abe nguSomajaji kuchubeka, kusho iWhite House ngeLisontfo.
Rosenstein usebenta njengemeluleki lokhetsekile Robert Mueller, lophenya ngekungenelela kweRussia elukhetfweni, budlelwane emkhatsini webasiti baTrump kanye neRussia kanye netinkinga letingaba khona tekwehlulela kwemengameli.
Kuleminyakanyaka leminyenti, iWashington beyikhuluma ngekutsi ngabe Trump utawamsusa yini uMmeli Jikelele, aphindze abeke bucotfo baMueller engotini.
Ekucaleni kwalenyanga, iNew York Times yabika kutsi Rosenstein wacoca ngekusetjentiswa kwetintambo tekubhala tinkhulumo naTrump kanye nekusebentisa luCwebu Lwesichibiyelo 25 kutsi amehlule.
Rosenstein uyakuphikisa loko.
Kodvwa ngeMsombuluko lowengcile waya eWhite House kute ayoshiya sikhundla sakhe.
Esikhundleni saloko, umhlangano wa-Trump lowawuse-UN eNew York, wamenyetelwa ngeLesine.
Trump watsi "bekangatsandza" kutsi angawucishi umhlangano wakhe, kepha lomhlangano wahlehliswa kute kugwenywe kuhlangana nelikomidi le-Senate Judiciary lapho khona Kavanaugh nalomunye walabasikati labambeka licala lekuhlukubeta ngekwelicasi, Dokotela Christina Blasey Ford, bafakaza.
NgaLesihlanu, Trump wayala kutsi kube neluphenyo lweliviki lonkhe loluphatselene netikhalo te-FBI ngaKavanaw, lokwenta kutsi kubambezeleke kakhulu kuvotelwa kweSigungu Savelonkhe.
Sikhulumi saTrump, Sarah Sanders, sakhuluma ku Fox News ngeLisontfo.
Ngesikhatsi abuzwa ngemhlangano wakhe naRosenstein, watsi: "Lilanga lemhlangano alikabekwa, kungenteka kutsi kutawuba kuleliviki, kepha kungenteka kutsi litawubekwa liviki linye ngenca yaletinye tentakalo letenteka enkantolo lephakeme".
Kodvwa sitawutibonela, futsi ngivame kukhetsa kugcina betindzaba bati.
Labanye babhali bayaphikisana nalombono: Sanders akazange ente tinkhulumo tekubika eWhite House kusukela ngaSeptemba 10.
Umsakazi wetfu Chris Wallace wabuta kutsi kungani.
Sanders utsi kungatfoli kwabo tinkhulumo akubangelwa "kubukela phansi umphakatsi" wetintfombi teTV, nanobe atsi: "Ngeke ngiphike kutsi bayadlala embikwebantfu".
Wakhutsata kutsi kwandziswe kubonana kwaTrump nemaphephandzaba.
"Mengameli uhlangana nebantfu labanyenti aphendvule imibuto yetintfombi kunanobe ngumuphi lomunye Mengameli", kwasho yena, angafuni kuniketa tinombolo leticondzile.
Sanders wacinisekisa kutsi tinkhulumo titawuchubeka, kodvwa nangabe betindzaba bakhona kubuta umengameli waseMelika imibuto ngalokucondzile, loko kuncono kakhulu kunekukhuluma nami.
Senta konkhe lokusemandleni etfu kutsi sente njalo, futsi niyati kutsi sibambe imihlangano leminyenti kangakanani kuleminyaka lembalwa leyengcile, futsi nangabe nikhona kukhuluma nemengameli waseMelika, loko kuyindlela lekahle yekubamba tinkhulumo temabhizinisi.
Trump uvame kuphendvula imibuto aphuma eWhite House, ahlangane nebantfu labanyenti nobe ahlanganyele netingcoco nebabhali.
Umhlangano wetindzaba kuphela - lokuyintfo lengavami.
Kutiphatsa kwemengameli lokukhululekile futsi lokungavamile kubetindzaba kuleliviki eNew York, kungaba yimpendulo yaloko.
Indvuna Yetemphilo Ibhalela Tisebenti Te-EU eScotland Ngenca Yekukhatsateka Nge-Brexit
INdvuna yetemphilo yatsi kubasebenti base-EU labasebenta e-Scotland, "Ngiyabonga kakhulu, ngicela kutsi bahlale etikhundleni tabo ngemuva kwe-Brexit".
Jean Freeman, MSP, wabhalela tisebenti takhe lesincwadzi sekusele tinyanga letingaphansi kwetisitfupha kutsi i-UK iphume e-EU.
Hulumende waseScotland sewutsintsene ngekubhadala tindleko tekufaka ticelo tetakhamuti te-EU letisebenta kuhulumende waso.
Encwadzini yakhe, Nkhosikati Freeman utsi: "Kuhlangana kwe-UK ne-EU mayelana nekuphuma kwachubeka ehlobo, futsi sincumo lesilindzelekile kumele sitfolakale kulenyanga.
Nanobe kunjalo, hulumende wase-UK uphindze wenta ncono kulungela simo lesingaba khona uma kungabi nalokutsintsekako.
Ngiyati kutsi lesi sikhatsi lesimatima kini nonkhe.
Ngako-ke, nyalo ngifuna kuphindze ngigcizelele kutsi ngiyawutsandza umsebenti lowentiwa nguwo wonkhe umuntfu, kungakhatsaliseki kutsi ubuya kuliphi live.
Bomake labasuka kulo lonkhe le-EU nangaphandle kwayo baletsa lwati lolubalulekile kanye nemakhono lacinisa aphindze ente ncono umsebenti wetemphilo futsi kuzuze tigulane nemiphakatsi lesiyisebentisako.
IScotland  likhaya lenu futsi sifuna nihlale khona.
Christian Abercrombie wahlindvwa ngekushesha ngenca yekulimala enhloko.
