Kutamatama Kwemhlaba Kanye Ne-Tsunami E-Indonesia
Ngekusho kwetiphatsimandla, lokungenani bantfu labangu-384 babulawa kutamatama kwemhlaba kanye netimvula temanti letinkhulu letishaye lidolobha lasePalu, e-Indonesia, ngaLesihlanu, futsi linani lebantfu labafile litawukhula.
Ngenca yekwehluleka kwekuhlanganisa, tisebenti tekuphepha atisitfoli sicondziso se-Donggal, indzawo lesenyakatfo yePalu, lesedvute nendzawo lokwenteka kuyo lomonakalo.
Bantfu labangetulu kwa-16 000 basuswa ePalu ngenca yenhlekelele yemvelo.
Nati letinye tintfo letibalulekile ngaPalu neDonggala, letiseSulawesi:
iPalu  lidolobha lelikhulu lesifundza sase Central Sulawesi, lisekugcineni kweligcuma lelimfisha elugwini lolusentshonalanga yeSulawesi Island, linebantfu labangu 379 800 (lokusho kutsi bekunebantfu labangu 2017)
Lelidolobha beligubha iminyaka lengu-40 likhona ngesikhatsi kutamatama kwemhlaba kanye ne-tsunami.
Donggala  sifundza lesilandzela emgceni welwandle longemakhilomitha lamakhulu lamatsatfu (180 ema mile) enyakatfo nshona yeSulawesi Island.
Le-county, indzawo lencane kunesifundza, nga 2017 beyinebantfu labangu 299 200.
Kudvweba kanye nekulima kusisekelo semnotfo wase Central Sulawesi, ikakhulukati endzaweni yase Donggala.
Umsebenti wekukhicita i-nickel nawo ubalulekile emnotfweni walesigodzi, kepha ugxile eMorawa, lolusebeleni loluphambene neSulawesi.
Ngekusho kwe-Indonesia Disaster Management Agency, ema-tsunami lamanyenti abhubhise ePalu naseDonggala kuleminyaka lengu-100 leyendlulile.
Nga-1938, tsunami yabulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-200 futsi yabhidlita emakhaya lamanyenti eDonggala.
Ema-tsunami aphindze aba khona enshonalanga yeDonggala nga-1996, abulala bantfu labasiphohlongo.
INdonesia isendzaweni lenemlilo lokutsiwa yiPacific Ring of Fire futsi ivame kutamatama kutamatama kwemhlaba.
Nati letinye tetindzawo letinyakatako kanye nema-tsunami lamanyenti lasebentile kuleminyaka lembalwa leyendlulile:
2004: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwenteka e-Indonesia, e-Aceh, enyakatfo yeSumatra, ngaDecember 26 kwabangela tsunami leyahlasela emave langu-14, kwabulala bantfu labangu-226,000 ngaselugwini lweLwandle lwaseNdiya, lokungaphezu kwehhafu yabo e-Aceh.
2005: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kwahlasela lentsentakusa yaseSumatra ngasentshonalanga ekupheleni kwaMarch nasekucaleni kwa-April.
Bantfu labanyenti bafa esihlengeni saseNyas, lesingaselugwini lwaseSumatra.
2006: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla langu-6.8 kwahlasela eningizimu yeJava, sihlenge lesinabantfu labanyenti e-Indonesia, kwabangela tsunami leyahlasela lentsetse leseningizimu, kwabulala bantfu labangaba ngu-700.
2009: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla langu-7,6 kwenteka ePadang, lokulidolobha lelikhulu lesifundza saseNtshonalanga yeSumatra.
Bantfu labangetulu kwa-1100 bafa.
2010: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla langu-7.5 kwahlasela siqhingi saseMentawai lesiseSumatra, kwabangela tsunami lebeyingaba ngemamitha langu-10 budze, leyabhidlita emadolobha lamanyenti yabulala bantfu labangaba ngu-300.
2016: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokuncane kwahlasela sifundza sasePidi-Jaya e-Acheche, kwabangela umonakalo kanye nekwesaba njengobe bantfu bakhumbula kutamatama kwemhlaba lokwabhubhisa kakhulu nga-2004 kanye ne-tsunami.
Nanobe kungakabi namtsunami, kwafa bantfu labangetulu kwa-100 ngenca yekubhidlika kwetakhiwo.
2018: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kwahlasela sihlenge sase-Indonesia iLombok, kwabulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-500, ikakhulukati enyakatfo.
Kutamatama kwemhlaba kwabhidlita takhiwo letinkhulungwane futsi kwabangela kutsi tivakashi letinyenti tihlale ngaphansi kwematje.
Indvodzana yaSara Palin lelidzala iboshwe ngesizatfu sekuhlukunyetwa ekhaya
Truck Palin, indvodzana lendzala ya Sarah Palin, lobekangumbusi wase-Alaska futsi lobekangumuntfu lobekafuna kuba lilunga leMengameli, waboshwa ngekuhlaselwa.
Palin, loneminyaka lengu-29 budzala waseWassilla, e-Alaska, waboshwa ngekusola budlova basemakhaya, kungenelela simo sekuhlukunyetwa, kanye nekumelana nekuboshwa, ngekusho kwemniningwane lowaphuma emaphoyiseni ase-Alaska ngeMgcibelo.
Ngekusho kwemibiko yemaphoyisa, lomunye umngani wakhe wetama kubita emaphoyisa kute amtjele ngebugebengu lobubhekwe kutsi buvele, wase uyamtsatsa.
Ngekusho kwe-KTUU, Palin usesejele laseMat-Su futsi utawukhishwa ngebheyili lengu-$500.
Wavela enkantolo ngeMgcibelo, futsi nakabutwa kutsi unelicala yini, watsi "akabi nacala".
Palin ubhekene nemacala lamatsatfu lalinganako, lokusho kutsi utawugwetjwa umnyaka munye ejele kanye ne-R250 000.
Uphindze abekwe licala lebugebengu belicembu B, lobuhambisana nekuboshwa lilanga linye kanye nekubhadala inhlawulo lengu-R2 000.
Lena akusiko kwekucala kutsi Palin abekwe emacala ebugebengu.
Ngenyanga yeNgongoni nga 2017 wabekwa licala lekuhlasela babe wakhe Todd Palin.
Unina, Sarah Palin, wabita emaphoyisa, wabikela kutsi kukhona lokutsiwa kuhlaselwa.
Lendzaba nyalo seyisenkantolo yema-veteran ase-Alaska.
NgaJanuwari 2016, wabekwa licala lekuhlukunyetwa ekhaya, lokwenta umbiko wekuhlukunyetwa emndenini kanye nekugcina sibhamu asebentisa tjwala ngenca yalendzaba.
Intfombi yakhe yatsi wayishaya buso.
Sarah Palin wagceka ngemacembu emaveteran nga 2016 ngemuva kwekuhlanganisa kutiphatsa kabi kwendvodzana yakhe ngekucindzeteleka lokwenteka ngemuva kwekushona kwakhe emphilweni lokwabangelwa kutsi abe asebenza e-Iraq.
Kutamatama Kwemhlaba Kanye Ne-Tsunami E-Indonesia: Bantfu Labanyenti Bafa
Lokungenani bantfu labangu-384 babulawa kutamatama kwemhlaba esihlengeni sase-Indonesia i-Sulawesi ngaLesihlanu.
Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla lafinyelela ku-7.5 kwabangela ema-tsunami futsi kwabhubhisa tinkhulungwane tetindlu.
Kugeleta nekuhlanganiswa kwetindzawo sekuphelile, futsi linani lebantfu labafile litawukhula kulamalanga letako.
Lokuzamazama kwemhlaba kwenteka edvute neSulawesi lesenyakatfo-mpumalanga yelidolobha lase-Indonesia iJakarta.
Ema-video alendzaba ayavela kubantfu labanyenti.
Bantfu labanyenti bebasePalu ngesikhatsi kutamatama tsunami.
Umshushisi wesive ufuna kuniketa umsolwa wekubulala waseNew York sigwebo sekufa lesingavami.
Umshushisi wesifundza waseNew York ufuna kufa kwaSayfullo Saipov, lobekwentiwa kutsi usole kuhlaselwa kwebantfu labasiphohlongo eNew York - sigwebo lesingavamile sebugebengu lobungekho ngaphasi kwemtsetfo waseMelika kusukela nga-1953.
Nga-Okthoba, Saipov, loneminyaka lengu-30 budzala, wacasha iloli le Home Depot kutsi lihlasele indlela yekugibela emabhayisikili eWest Side Highway eLower Manhattan, libulala bantfu labahamba ngetinyawo kanye nebagibeli bemabhayisikili.
Kute kucinisekiswe kutsi sigwebo sekufa sicinisekisiwe, bashushisi batawudzinga kuveta kutsi Saipov "wabulala bantfu labasiphohlongo ngenhloso" futsi "walimata bantfu ngalokungenhloso", ngekusho kwencwadzi yesatiso lesendluliselwe eSouthern District yaseNew York.
Ngekusho kwemibhalo yasenkantolo, lamacala lamabili angenta kutsi sigwebo sekufa sibekwe.
Ngemuva kwemaviki lambalwa ngemuva kwekuhlaselwa, lijaji lelikhulu le-federal lafaka Saipov emacala langu-22 lafaka ekhatsi emacala lasiphohlongo ekubulala ngekuhunga, lavame kusetjentiswa batameli bangaphasi kwemtsetfo emacaleni ebugebengu lobuhlelekile, kanye nekusebentisa budlova nekubhubhisa timoto.
Ngekusho kwebaphikisi, lokuhlasela bekuhlelwe ngekucophelela futsi ngekuhlakanipha, futsi Saipov wakwenta ngendlela leyenyanyekako, lenelunya kanye neyekugebenga.
Saifulo Habibullayevich Saipov wabangela kulimala, umonakalo kanye nekulahlekelwa emindenini nakubangani ba-Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Lora Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erli, Ernan Ferrucci, Ernan Diego Mendoza kanye na-Alejandro Damiano Pagnocco, kusho satiso setinhloso.
Laba labasihlanu labafa bekutindzawo tekuvakasha tase-Argentina.
Sekuphele iminyaka lelishumi kusukela ngesikhatsi umshushisi waseNingizimu New York afuna sigwebo sekufa.
NgaSeptemba 2009, ummangalelwa Khalid Barnes watfolwa anelicala lekubulala batsengisi betidzakamiva lababili, kepha wagcine agwetjwe kuphila kwakhe konkhe ejele.
Kugwetjwa kwekugcina kwebantfu lababulawa e-New York kwaba nga-1953 kuJulius na-Ethel Rosenberg, bantfu labashadile lababulawa ngekuhlanganyela ekuhloleni i-Soviet Union ngesikhatsi semphi lebandzako eminyakeni lemibili leyendlulile.
BoRosenberg babulawa ngekusebentisa situlo semandla mhlaka 19 Inhlaba 1953.
Ngekusho kwemiculu yenkantolo, Saipov, lowatalwa e-Uzbekistan, akazange aphendvuke ngemuva kwekuhlaselwa.
Ngekusho kwemaphoyisa, watjela baphenyi kutsi uyajabula ngekwenta loko.
Ngekusho kwalesicelo, Saipov watjela tiphatsimandla kutsi waciniswa kutsi ente lokuhlasela ngekubuka i-ISIS ku-phone yakhe.
Waphindze wacela kutsi kufakwe ifulegi ye-ISIS egumbini lakhe lesibhedlela, kusho emaphoyisa.
Uphika emanga kuto tonkhe tizatfu letingu-22 talenkhulumo.
David Patton, longulomunye webameli bemphakatsi labavikela Saipov, watsi badvumatekile ngesincumo selihhovisi lemshushisi.
"Sifuna kutsi sigwebo sekufa kunekutsi sigwetjwe imphilo yonkhe ngaphandle kwekukhululeka, sicedze buhlungu lobukhulu lobubangelwa nguletintfo kubo bonkhe bantfu", kusho Patton.
Bavikeli ba Saipov bebatfole sicelo kubashushisi kutsi bangayi kujeziswa.
Lilunga lePhalamende le-Tory litsi Nigel Farage akukafaneli abe nemtfwalo wekukhuluma nge-Brexit
Ngesikhatsi sekuvukela umhlangano wemaTori lamuhla, Nigel Farage wafunga kutsi "utawufaka umbutfo webantfu".
Umholi wangaphambilini we-UKIP watsi bosopolitiki kufanele "batinake" bantfu labangatsandzi i-EU, ngobe lilunga lephalamende la Theresa May lisho kutsi nguye lobekufanele abambe lichaza ekucociseni ne-EU.
Umuntfu lolilunga lelicembu le-Conservative Peter Bone, watsi emhlanganweni waseBirmingham, i-UK "beyingakuphuma" kube uMnumzane Farage bekangumabhalane we-Brexit.
