"Sifaka umbutfo webantfu kulelive lelisinikete kuncoba e-Brexit, futsi angeke siphumelele size sibe yi-United Kingdom letimele, leticinile futsi letigcabhako".
Ngesikhatsi lesifanako, labaphikisana ne-Brexit bahamba nemiboniso eBirmingham, ngemuva kwaloko baba nemhlangano wema-awa lamabili enkabeni yedolobha.
Tikhungo letinyenti betiphakamisa tibhebhe letitsi "Tories against Brexit" kuleliviki.
