Bantfu laba batsi bangakhona kwenta tinhlelo te-IT kanye ne-Canada plus plus, kutsi tisebente eminyeleni, kutsi tihwebe mahhala ngaphandle kwemincele ne-Ireland, wachubeka watsi.
Loku kungumdlalo loyedvwa.
Utsi "i-Brexit lenhle ayikho".
