I-Grand Prix yaseRussia: Lewis Hamilton usondzela esicongweni selibhola lemhlaba ngemuva kwekutsi indlela yakhe yekudlala inike inhlulo ku-Sebastian Fettel
Kusukela ngesikhatsi Valtteri Bottas ahamba embili kuLwesihlanu, ahamba embili kuLewis Hamilton, kwacaca kutsi indlela yelicembu le-Mercedes itawudlala indzima lenkhulu kulomncintiswano.
Bottas wacala kahle kusuka ku-pole position futsi wacishe wahlala eHamilton ngesikhatsi avikela indzawo yakhe emajikeni lamabili ekucala, futsi wamema Fettel kutsi ahlasele umlingani wakhe.
