Mercedes wahamba waya emgodzini ngemuva kwemjikelo munye, wase uyaphuma ngemuva kwa Fettel, kepha Hamilton, ngemuva kwekulwa kancane, wacala kuhamba, lokwenta kutsi umshayeli we Ferrari angavumi kushiya indzawo yangekhatsi, aphatamiseka ngemuva kwekusebenta kabili ekuvikeleni ngekugucuka kwesitsatfu.
Ngelilanga lakhe lekutala le-21, Max Ferstappen wacala kusuka ngemuva emgceni welibhola futsi bekasesikhundleni sesikhombisa ekupheleni kweligaba lekucala.
