Mengameli Donald Trump wagceka i-Senator Diane Feinstein emhlanganweni webavoti ngeMgcibelo ngekusho kwakhe kutsi akazange ayishicelele incwadzi yaChristina Blasey Ford leyabeka Brett Kavanaugh, lofuna kuba lijaji lelikhulu, licala lekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicasi.
