British Elite Hockey League: Dandy Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ushayele emaGiants emagoli lamabili emdlalweni wabo neDundee.
Emdlalweni we Elite Hockey League, i-Dundee Stars yabhadala ngekulahlekelwa yi-Belfast Giants ngeLesihlanu, ngekuncoba umdlalo wayo wekuphindzisela ngeMgcibelo nga-5-3 ku-Dundee.
EmaGiants atfola buhle bekucala ngemagoli lamabili ngekushaya kwaPatrick Dwyer naFrancis Bovillier.
Mike Sullivan na Jordan Cooney baphakamisa lizinga lelicembu lelikhaya ngaphambi kwekutsi Dwyer ahole emaGiants.
Francois Bouchar wafananisa inombolo ye Dundee ngaphambi kwekutsi imigca lemibili yaLundwald Nielsen icinise kuncoba kwabo.
Kulabantfu ba-Adam Keefe, labancoba i-Dundee 2:1 eBelfast ngeLesihlanu kusihlwa, kwaba kuncishiswa kwesitsatfu kulesizini ye-Elite League.
Loku bekungumhlangano wesine emkhatsini walamacembu kulesizini, ngesikhatsi emaGiants ancobe imidlalo yawo lemitsatfu leyengcile.
Inhloso yekucala yaDwayer yafika emaminithini lamane ngemuva kwa 3:35 ngemuva kwekudlula kwaKendall McFall ngekwesekelwa nguDavid Rutherford, ngemuva kwaloko Bovillier waphindza kabili ngemuva kwemaminithi lamane.
Ngesikhatsi sekuchubeka kwalesikhatsi, Sullivan wabuyisela labamemile emuva emdlalweni nga 13:10, ngaphambi kwekutsi Matt Markwardt asite Cooney ekudlaleni.
Dwyer wacinisekisa kutsi iGiants itsatsa sinyatselo ngesikhatsi sekuphumula kwekucala ngesikhatsi afaka umgomo wesibili kusihlwa ekupheleni kwesikhatsi sekucala.
Bekufanele baphindze bahlangane futsi, futsi Bouchard waphindze walinganisa sibalo, wafaka umgomo ngesikhatsi banesabelo lesiphakeme sa 27:37.
Cooney na Charles Corcoran bahlangana kute basite Nielsen kutsi anikete Dundee litfuba lekucala emdlalweni kutsi atsatse bukhosi ekupheleni kwesikhatsi sesibili, ngemuva kwaloko yena nelicembu lakhe bacinisa kuncoba, bagcina balingani babo basemkhatsini wenkambu kuze kuphele sikhatsi sekugcina.
EmaGiants, lasandza kulahlekelwa yimidlalo lemine kulengu-5 yekugcina, aya eMilton Keynes emdlalweni wawo lolandzelako, lotawubanjwa ngaLesihlanu.
