Ngekucaphuna etinhlotjeni te-Ministry of Justice, Park Byung Seung watsi kusukela nga-2011 bekunetigameko letingu-2706 tekubaleka, kodvwa nga-2015, letibalo setehle taba ngu-1127.
Umnumzane Park utsi tintfo letibalulekile kubekwa kweluhlelo lwekugadza umncele emkhatsini weNyakatfo Korea ne China kanye netindleko letisetulu letikhokhiswa batsengisi betimphahla.
I-Pyongyang ayitsatsi sincumo emphakatsini.
Labanyenti labakhoseli baseNyakatfo yeKorea bagcine sebaniketwe buve baseNingizimu.
Seoul itsi kusukela kwaphela imphi yaseKorea nga-1953, bantfu labangetulu kwa-30 000 baseNyakatfo Korea bewele umnyele ngalokungekho emtsetfweni.
Bantfu labanyenti babaleka badzabula eChina, lenemncele lomudze kakhulu neNyakatfo Korea, lokulula kuwuhlangabeta kunendzawo levikelekile yekulwa nemasotja (i-DMZ) emkhatsini wemaKorea lamabili.
I-China ibuka lababaleki njengebantfu labangekho emtsetfweni, hhayi njengetihambi, futsi ivame kubabuyisela ekhaya ngenkhani.
Budlelwane emkhatsini weNyakatfo neNingizimu, lobusolo busemphini, butfutfuke kakhulu etinyangeni letimbalwa letengcile.
