Indlela imphi yekuhwebelana neMelika lengaba lusito ngayo eBeijing
Labati kutsi lemphi yekuhweba emkhatsini weMelika ne China beyimangalisa, futsi nanobe lemphi isengakapheli, kwehlukana emkhatsini wemave kungazuzisa iBeijing esikhatsini lesidze.
Donald Trump, Mengameli waseMelika, wakhipha secwayiso sakhe sekucala ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, ngekubeka umtselo etikwetintfo letinkhulu tase China letitsengiswa ngaphandle, kufaka ekhatsi emabhethri elanga, insimbi ne aluminium.
Lokunyakata kakhulu kwenteka kuleliviki, ngesikhatsi ematharifi lamasha enta umonakalo wetintfo letingu-$200 billion (£150 billion), lokusho kutsi cishe incenye yaloko lokungeniswa eMelika kusuka eChina, kwafakwa intsela.
I-Beijing ihlale ibuyisela, muva nje ibeke intsela lelingemaphesenti lasihlanu kuya kulalishumi etintfweni letitinkhulungwane temadola latinkhulungwane letinge-60 temarandi letitfunyelwa eMelika.
I-China yetsembise kutsi itawuphindzisela i-USA ngalokulinganako futsi umnotfo wesibili lomkhulu emhlabeni angeke ube netinkinga ngekushesha.
Kucindzetela iWashington kutsi ihambe emuva kusho kunikela ngetimfuno, kepha kunikela e-USA embikwebantfu kungaba lihlazo kakhulu ku-Xi Jinping, Mengameli wase China.
Nanobe kunjalo, tati titsi uma iBeijing ingakhona kudlala kahle emakhadi ayo, kucindzetelwa yimphi yekuhwebelana yaseMelika kungasekela iChina sikhatsi lesidze, kunciphisa kutsembela kwemnotfo wato.
Loku kutsi sincumo lesisheshe sentiwe eWashington nobe eBeijing singenta simo lesingaholela ekuvalweni kwemnotfo kunobe nguliphi live, kuyingoti kakhulu kunaloko lokwatiswa ngulababukeli, kusho Abigail Grace, lososayensi wase-Asia e-Center for New American Security.
