Lwandle lolubovu: tindzaba Kugcwala kwetintfo letincane kwehla ePinellas, eManati naseSarasota
Umbiko lomusha we Florida Fish and Wildlife Commission ukhombisa kwehla lokukhulu kwemandla emanti lamnyama etindzaweni letitsite tase Tampa Bay.
Ngekusho kwe-FWC, tindzawo tase Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte nase Collier County tibika kutsi tihlume kakhulu, lokusho kutsi kunekuncishiswa kwetintfo letincane letiphila emmangweni.
Lendzawo lenkhulu iRed Tide ihlanganisa emabhange langu 130 kusuka enyakatfo yePinnell kuya eningizimu yeLee County.
Letindzawo letincane tekubhekana netinkinga tingabonakala cishe emamayeleni langu-10 kusuka elugwini lwaseHillsborough, kepha tibe tincane kakhulu kunangesontfo lowengcile.
Lamagelebisi labovu aphindze abonwa ePasco County.
Kuleliviki leliphelile, kubikwe kutsi kunemkhawulo lomkhulu e-Pinellas County nasetindzaweni letisedvute nayo, kusuka kumkhawulo lophansi kuya kumkhawulo lomkhulu e-Hillsborough County, umkhawulo lomkhulu e-Manatee nase-Sarasota County nasetindzaweni letisemnceleni, umkhawulo lomkhulu e-Charlotte County, umkhawulo lomkhulu e-Lee County, kanye nemkhawulo lomncane e-Collier County.
Emaveni lafana ne Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee kanye ne Collier, kusenekwenteka kutsi kube nekucindzeteleka kwetindlela tekuphefumula.
Kute lokwatiswa lokumayelana naloko lokwenteka enyakatfo-nshonalanga yeFlorida evikini leliphelile.
